Emalunga emaPhalamende aseWelsh akhatsateke ngekutsi atawudideka ngekutsi angemaMuppet
Lamanye emalunga ephalamende aveta kukhatsateka kwawo mayelana nesiphakamiso sekuntjintja sicu sawo sibe yi-MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament  Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Lesimo sekukhatsateka savela macondzana netinhlelo tekuntjintja ligama lemhlangano wePhalamende yaseWales.
Emalunga eliPhalamende kulo lonkhe lelive akhatsateke ngekutsi loku kutawusho kutsi kuyahlekisa.
Lenye incenye yeLicembu Letemisebenti yatsi licembu layo likhatsatekile kutsi "litawufana nemavi latsi Twp na Pwp".
Kubala labangasiwo emaWelsh: NgesiWelsh, ligama lelitsi "twp" lisho "kuhlazeka" kantsi ligama lelitsi "pwp" lisho "kulahlwa".
Lilunga le-MP lelisePlainide latsi lelicembu "alijabuli" futsi laphakamisa letinye tindlela.
Lenye inhlangano yemaWelsh leyayinemibono leyehlukile yatsi licembu layo "belifuna kwati" ngekuguculwa kweligama, kepha yaphawula kutsi leligama lelitsi MWP aliveli kakhulu kuleligama lelitsi "muppet".
Kulombhalo, le Welsh w ibitwa ngendlela lefana ne Yorkshire English ye u.
Likomidi lePhalamende, lelisungula umtsetfosivivinyo wekuntjintjwa kwelibito, latsi: "Lincumo leliphelele mayelana nekutsi ngabe libizo lelitsini leli litawubitwa yini, kutawuba yincumo yebavoti".
UMtsetfo waHulumende waseWales wanga-2017 unikete iPhalamende yaseWales emandla ekushintja ligama layo.
NgaJuni, liKhomishani latfumela imiphumela yekubonisana nemphakatsi mayelana netiphakamiso letemukelwe kabanti tekutsi leliphalamende libitwa ngekutsi yiPhalamende yaseWales.
Mayelana nesihloko seMalunga, liKhomishani likhetse ligama lelitsi 'Lilunga lePhalamende yaseWales' nobe i-WMP, kepha kukhetsa kwe-MWP ngiko lokutfole kwesekelwa lokukhulu kulolucwaningo lolwentiwe.
Emalunga eliKhomishani leMengameli ngekusobala ahle ahlela letinye tindlela, kepha kutfola imvumo yekusebentisa leligama kungaba yintfo lematima kuSihlalo wePhalamende, Ellen Jones, lokumele etfule umtsetfo wekuntjintja leligama emavikini letako.
Umtsetfo wetingucuko utawufaka ekhatsi letinye tingucuko endleleni lephalamende lesebentako ngayo, kufaka ekhatsi imitsetfo yekwesula lilunga lephalamende esikhundleni kanye nekuhlelwa kweluhlelo lwekomiti.
Emalunga eMkhandlu loweNgamele atawutsatsa sincumo sekuhlela livoti lekugcina mayelana nekutsi atawubitwa njani uma kucocwa ngemitsetfo.
