Tinkhulumo taseSt. Martin tiye tancipha njengobe emasontfo aseHarlem ayanyamalala
"Bantfu labadzala lengikhulume nabo batsi bekunelibha kanye nelibandla emagumbini onkhe", kwasho Mnu. Adams.
Lamuhla, kute lokubili".
Watsi uyasibona sizatfu sekunyamalala kwaletindzawo tekudlela.
Watsi: "Bantfu lamuhla bahlanganyela nalabanye bantfu ngendlela leyehlukile".
"Titafula akusasiyo indzawo yekuhlala yakini lapho bantfu bahlangana khona njalo".
Mayelana nemabandla, ukhatsateke ngekutsi imali leyitfolakala ngekutsengiswa kwetintfo angeke ihlale sikhatsi lesidze njengobe bantfu labatsite "kufanele babuyele lapho bacala khona".
Wengeta watsi emabandla angashintjwa ngemakhaya lamakhulu lagcwele bantfu labangeke bafune kusita tindzawo tekukhontela letisele emimangweni.
"Linyenti lebantfu labatawutsenga tindlu kuletikhungo litawuba ngema-white", washo njalo, "ngako-ke kutawusheshisa lilanga lapho onkhe lamabandla atawuvalwa ngalokuphelele, ngobe akukafaneli kutsi bonkhe bantfu labatawungena kuletikhungo babe ngemalunga alelibandla".
Totimbili letilibandla takhiwa ngemabandla ebantfu labamhlophe ngaphambi kwekutsi iHarlem ibe yindzawo yebantfu labamnyama - i-Metropolitan Community yakhiwa nga-1870, iSt Martin yakhiwa ngemuva kweminyaka lelishumi.
Lelibandla lebuMethodist lekucala lahlubuka nga-1930.
Libandla lebantfu labamnyama lebelilapho, lacala kutsatsa lesakhiwo.
Lesakhiwo saseSt. Martin satfunjwa libandla lebantfu labamnyama lebeliholwa nguMfundisi John Howard Johnson, lowamisa sitolo lesise-125 Street, lokuyindlela lebalulekile yekutsengisa eHarlem, lebesala kubeka bantfu labamnyama emsebentini nobe batfutfukiswe.
Umlilo wanga-1939 walimata lendlu, kodvwa bafundisi baMfundisi Johnson bacala kwakha kabusha futsi bacela kutsi kwakhiwe lendlu.
Umfundisi David Johnson, indvodzana yaBabe Johnson kanye nendlalifa yakhe esontfweni laseSt. Martin, ngekutigcabha wabita leligubhu ngekutsi "timemeteli tebantfu labaphuyile".
Leso sisebenti lesasenta lomdlalo ngaJulayi, sachaza lelicembu ngalenye indlela: "lifa lemasiko" kanye "nesitfombe lesingagucuki semlandvo".
Leso sifundvo, lesentiwa nguTiffany Inn waseNyuvesi yaseMichigan, saphindze saveta kutsi bekuli-carillon yekucala emhlabeni wonkhe leyayidlalwa ngumhlabeli lomnyama, Dionysius A. Lind, lowatfutsela ku-carillon lenkhulu eRiberside Church eminyakeni lengu-18 leyendlulile.
Umnumzane Merriweather watsi lisontfo laseSt. Martin alizange limtsatse esikhundleni sakhe.
Lokuchubekako etinyangeni letimbalwa letendlulile eSanta Martin, kuyindzaba lematima emkhatsini wetakhi netakhiwonchanti, labanye babo bacashwe baholi beliBandla labavamile, kantsi labanye bacashwa baholi bemabandla.
