Emacebo aseSainsbury's enta kutsi imakethe yetintfo tekuhloba yase-UK ibe netinkinga
I-Sainsbury's iyaphikisana neBoots, i-Superdrug ne-Debenhams ngekubeka ema-shelf etitolo letitsite, letiphetfwe bacashi labanelikhono.
Njengencenye yekukhula lokukhulu kwemakethe yetintfo tekuhloba yase UK lelinganiselwa ku- Â£2.8 billion, lesolo ikhula ngesikhatsi imiculu yetintfo tekugcoka kanye netintfo tasekhaya ihamba kancane, emashalofu lamakhulu etintfo tekuhloba atawufakwa etitolo letingu-11 eveni lonkhe, bese kutsi uma kuphumelela, asakateke kuletinye.
Kutjala imali etitolo letitsengisa tintfo tekuhloba kuta njengobe timakethe letinkhulu tifuna tindlela tekugcwalisa emashalofini labekadze akhokha ema-TV, ema-microwave kanye netimphahla tasekhaya.
Sainsbury's itsi itawuphindzaphindza linani lemikhicito yayo yetintfo tekuhloba ibe ngemikhicito lengu-3 000, kufaka ekhatsi imikhicito lefana neRevlon, Essie, Tweezerman kanye neDr. PawPaw kwekucala.
Emarike lakhona e-L'Oreal, Maybelline kanye ne-Burt's Bees nawo atawuniketwa indzawo lenkhulu ngemashelufu laneluphawu lwenkampani, lafana nalawo etitolo letifana neBoots.
Lesitolo siphindze sicale kabusha luhlu lwetitfombe letitsite letitsite kute kutsi tintfo letinyenti tibe nguletitsandvwa bantfu labadzala - lokuyintfo lefunwa kakhulu ngulabasebentisi labasha.
Ngetulu kwaloko, inkampani yephunga i-Fragrance Shop itawetama kutfola imikhicito yayo etitolo letimbili te-Sainsbury's, lesinye lesisandza kuvula eCroydon, eNingizimu London, ngeliviki leliphelile, kantsi lesinye sisuke sivuleka eShelly Oak, eBirmingham, ngekuhamba kwalomnyaka.
Kutsenga lokuku-Internet kanye nekutsenga kudla lokuncane malanga onkhe etitolo letincane, kusho kutsi timakethe letinkhulu kumele tente imetamo lemikhulu yekwenta bantfu kutsi bavakashele.
Mike Cope, umphatsi lomkhulu weSainsbury's, watsi titolo letitsengisa tintfo letitsite titawufana netitolo letitsengisa tintfo letitsite, njengobe emachinga etitolo letitsengisa tintfo letitsite etama kuchudzelana netitolo letitsengisa tintfo letitsite letitsite letitsite letinjenge-Aldi ne-Lidl ngetintfo letitsite letingasiyo yekudla.
Sainsbury's ifake ema-Argos outlet emakhulwini etitolo, iphindze ifake naletinye titolo i-Habitat njengoba yatsenga letinhlangano letimbili eminyakeni lemibili leyengcile, lokwenta kutsi kutsengiswa kwetintfo tekudla kube ncono futsi kwenta kutsenga kube yinzuzo.
Umzamo waso wekuvuselela tindzawo tekuhlobisa kanye netemitsi waphela.
Sainsbury's yetama kusebenta ndzawonye neBoots ekucaleni kwa-2000s, kepha lolubambiswano lwaphela ngemuva kwekuphikisana mayelana nendlela yekuhambisa inzuzo etitolo temitsi kuletitolo letinkhulu.
Lendlela lensha yakhiwa ngemuva kwekutsi iSainsbury's itsengise ibhizinisi yayo yetitolo letingu 281 ku Celesio, umnikati we Lloyds Pharmacy, ngemali lengemarandi langu 125 eminyakeni lemitsatfu leyengcile.
Watsi iLloyds itawudlala indzima yayo kuloluhlelo, ngekwengeta linani lelikhulu letigcoko letitsandzekako, kufaka ekhatsi iLa Roche-Posay neVichy, kuletitolo letine.
Paul Mills-Hicks, umcondzisi wekutsengisa weSainsbury's, watsi: "Sishintjile indlela emashalofu etfu labukeka ngayo kute sente simo sibe ncono kubatsengi betfu.
Siphindze futsi sacala kusebentisa bantfu labaceceshwe kahle kute basite bantfu labatsite.
Inombolo yetinkampani tetfu yakhiwe ngendlela yekutsi ihlangabetane nato tonkhe tidzingo, kantsi simo lesihle kanye netindzawo letikahle kusho kutsi nyalo sesiphindze sibe yindzawo lencono yekuhambisa tintfo tekuhlobisa letibukene nendlela yesintfu yekutsenga".
