Lomake loneminyaka lengu-44 budzala watfolakala nga-7:55 ekuseni anesilondza semukhwa eGrayson Mews kuJohn Street, kantsi indvodza leneminyaka lengu-32 budzala, iboshiwe ngesizatfu sekufa.
Emaphoyisa acele bantfu bakulesigodzi labake babona nobe beva lokutsite kutsi bakubike emaphoyiseni.
Siphatsimandla Brian O'Hagan sitsi: "Lolucwaningo selusesigabeni sekucala kodvwa ngitsandza kucela nobe ngubani lobekasendzaweni yaseJohn Street lobone nobe weva lokutsite lokungahle kubonakale kutsi kuyenteka, kutsi asitjele.
Ngicela kutsi nobe ngubani, ikakhulukati bashayeli bamatekisi, labangatsintseka ngekubamba lemibono, asitsintse njengobe banelwati lolubalulekile eluphenyo lwetfu".
Liphoyisa licinisekise kutsi lomfati lobekafile bekangumhlali waseBirkenhead futsi watfolakala asesitokisini.
Ngalolosuku ntsambama bangani labatsatsa ngekutsi bayamati lomake bafika endzaweni yalobugebengu kute babute imibuto mayelana nendzawo lapho atfolwe khona ngalelolanga ekuseni.
Lucwaningo luyachubeka njengoba emaphoyisa atsi asebenta ngekwatisa tihlobo.
