Bahlali batjelwa kutsi kungatsatsa ema-awa ngaphambi kwekutsi bavunyelwe kubuyela emakhaya abo.
Liphoyisa latsi litjele lendvodza kutsi lendzawo yonkhe seyiyindzawo yekuhlaselwa.
Lomunye umfati wavela ethendeni, akhala.
Bekaphindze atsi, "Kwesabeka".
