Ngesikhatsi lesifanako, indzawo lenemimoya lenemandla lamancane seyivele seyivele yakheka ngetulu kweLwandle iPacific, iya ngasemphumalanga yeLwandle lwaseNshonalanga yaseMelika. Njengobe lesiphepho lesinguRosa sisondzela eSichingi saseCalifornia ngeMsombuluko, siphepho lesinemandla lamakhulu sitawuletsa bumantana lobunetimphepho enyakatfo yeNingizimu Melika.
