Ngemuva kwaloko, bumantana lobusetulu lobuhlangene nelizinga lemanti laphasi lelisondzela, kutawubangela imvula lenkhulu eningizimu-nshonalanga kulamalanga lambalwa letako.
Imvula lencane lengaba ngemasentimitha langu-2,5 kuya ku-10 ingenta kutsi kube netikhukhula letiyingoti, tindvundvuma kanye nekugcumagcuma.
Lomswakama lowesabekako lowesabekako utawuholela ekumeni kwemvula lengaba ngemasentimitha lasihlanu kuya kulasikhombisa ngeli-awa etindzaweni letinyenti, ikakhulukati etincenyeni taseNevada leseNingizimu nase-Arizona.
Imvula lecishe ibe ngemasentimitha lasihlanu kuya kulasitfupha, iyahlelwa eSouthwest, ikakhulukati e-Arizona.
Kuyagcwala futsi kungahle kube netimvula letisheshako ngenca yekubandza kwetimvula letinemandla.
Kunconywa kutsi uvikele nobe ngabe ngukuphi kuhamba ngetinyawo ehlane ngenca yesimo semvula lesetfwasa emhlabatsini.
Imvula lenkhulu ingenta emagcuma abe tinsiba temanti, futsi emagagasi angenta kutsi kube nemoya lomkhulu kanye nesihlabatsi.
Lendzawo lenemoya lonemandla kakhulu itawubangela kutsi kube netimvula letinkhulu endzaweni letsite leseNingizimu yeCalifornia.
Kutawubakhona imvula lenkhulu lengetulu kwesentimitha, lokungabangela kutsi kube netindvonga letincane kanye nekugedvuka emigwacweni.
