Bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-20 babukela kucocwa kwaBret Kavanaugh
Bangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-20 bantfu labebabukele inkhulumo leyetfulwa nguBret Kavanaugh, lobekafuna kuba lijaji leNkantolo lePhakeme yaseMelika, ngaLesine, kanye nalomake lowamsola ngekumhlukubeta, lokwatfolakala kutsi kwenteka nga-1980, Christine Blaisey Ford, ngetinkhulumo te-TV letisitfupha.
Kantsi-ke, lesimo lesimatima lesitsintsa tindzaba tepolitiki, sichubeka, netinhlelo te-TV tavala luhlelo lwato lolutawuchubeka lwekucedza lomsebenti ngeLesihlanu: kuvumelana kweSigungu lesengamele sase-Arizona, Jeff Flake, kutsi kube neluphenyo lweliviki lonkhe lwe-FBI mayelana naletimangalo.
Ford watjela likomidi lebucotfo kutsi ucinisile kutsi ngesikhatsi basesikolweni, Kavanaugh wamhlasela futsi wetama kumehlisa.
Kavanaugh, embikweni wakhe loligugu, watsi ucinisekile kutsi loko akuzange kwenteke.
Ngekusho kwe-Nielsen, bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-20.4 babukela leliviki lelishumi.
Le-Insta ye-TV yabala lizinga lekubuka kuthelevishini ku-CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel kanye ne-MSNBC.
Tinombolo atizange titfolakale masinyane kuletinye tinhlelo letatfumela lomlayeto, kufaka ekhatsi i-PBS, i-C-SPAN ne-Fox Business Network.
I-Nielsen ivame kuba nenkinga yekubalwa kwebantfu labakubukelako kusakata emahhovisi.
Kute sibukele kahle, kubukela lokutsite kutawufanana nekubuka umdlalo webhola lelishisako nobe umcimbi we-Oscar.
I-Fox News, leyatfola kusekelwa lokukhulu kwe-Kavano, yahola ngekulinganiselwa kwetigidzi letingu-5.69 ngesikhatsi sekubukwa kwemalanga onkhe, ngekusho kwe-Nielsen.
Kantsi endzaweni yesibili, i-ABC inebantfu labangu-3.26 wetigidzi.
I-CBS ilandzelwe ngu-3.1 million, i-NBC ilandzelwe ngu-2.94 million, i-MSNBC ilandzelwe ngu-2.89 million, i-CNN ilandzelwe ngu-2.52 million, ngekusho kwe-Nielsen.
Bantfu labanyenti bebavusa inkhutsalo ngemuva kwekuva umbiko.
Flake wavela njengendlalifa lenkhulu ku- Friday night live.
Ngemuva kwekusho kwalabamnene kutsi batawuvota, i-CNN ne-CBS yakhipha sitfombe ngeLesihlanu ekuseni, lapho bekunebantfu labamcansulako njengobe beketama kungena ku-elevator kute ayewuviwa yiKomiti yeTebulungiswa.
Wema eme embikwebantfu imizuzu leminyenti ngesikhatsi bamsola, babukela i-CNN.
Lomunye umfati watsi: "Ngimi lapha embikwenu.
"Uyakholelwa yini kutsi ukhuluma liciniso kulelive?
Watsi: "Unemandla nangabe bafati labanyenti bangakhoni kwenta loko".
Flake watsi lihhovisi lakhe selikhiphe sitatimende, futsi ngaphambi kwekutsi kuvalwe iminyango yelithende, watsi utawuba nalokunyenti langakusho enkantolo.
Tonkhe tinhlelo te-TV netekusakaza betibukela live ema-awa lambalwa ngemuva kwaloko, kuvotelwa kweLikomidi Letebulungiswa leSigungu Lesikhulu mayelana nekukhutsata kubekwa kwaKavana kutsi abe lilunga leSigungu Lesikhulu.
Flake watsi utawenta loko kuphela nangabe i-FBI icwaninga ngetindzaba letimelene nalomuntfu lotawuba ngumengameli kuleliviki lelitako, lokwacelwa linani lelikhulu lemaDemocrats.
Flake wacinisekiswa kancane kancane ngemuva kwekubonisana nemngani wakhe, losincumo se-Democratic, Chris Koons.
Ngemuva kwekubonisana naKunes kanye nalamanye emalunga eNkantolo lephakeme, Flake wakhipha sincumo.
Lokukhetsa kwaFlake bekusebenta ngobe bekubonakala shengatsi emaRiphabliki abengeke akhone kucinisekisa kutsi uMtsetfosivivinyo we-Cavano uyaphumelela ngaphandle kwekutsi kwentiwe lucwaningo.
Mengameli Trump ucele i-FBI kutsi iphenye ngetindzaba letashiwo nga Kavanaugh.
