Umcondzisi wetemidlalo we-LSU, Joey Aleva, wabonga umtsetfo wasekhaya ngekwenta "lucwaningo lolucophelwe kahle kanye nekuphatsa kahle".
Sims abeneminyaka lengu-20 budzala.
