Bantfu labasitfupha baboshwa ngeMgcibelo eBarcelona ngemuva kwekushayisana kwebabhikishi labafuna inkhululeko kanye nemaphoyisa, ngesikhatsi tinkhulungwane tebantfu tihlanganyela emicimbini yekugubha umnyaka wekucala wevoti le-Catalonia yekutikhetsela.
Licembu lebantfu lebebambetse timphahla tekutitsandzela, lelabanjwa ngemaphoyisa, lalahla emacandza kanye nelitfuli lelibolile, lakhicita litfuli lelimnyama lelimnyama emigwacweni levame kugcwala tivakashi.
Kubambana kwaphindze kwaba khona emini ngesikhatsi emaphoyisa asebentisa emabhasikidi abo kute acedze kubambana.
Ema-awa lamanyenti emacembu ebantfu labatsandza inkhululeko yaseCatalonia akhuluma ngesihloko lesitsi "Asikhohlwa, Asitsetseleli" nakubhekiswe kumacembu ebantfu labatsandza kuhlangana kulelive labamemeta batsi "Aliphile iSpain".
Bantfu labalishumi nakune balashwa ngetingoti letincane letenteka ngesikhatsi semibhikisho, ngekusho kwemaphephandzaba.
Tinkinga tisaphakama kulesigodzi lesisekela inkhululeko, ngemuva kwemnyaka munye kusukela uMadrid amemetele kutsi lenkhombandlela ya-October 1 ingekho emtsetfweni, kodvwa-ke, le-referendum igubha bantfu baseCatalan labamelela inkhululeko.
Linyenti lelabakhetsile lakhetsa inkhululeko, nanobe kuvota bekuphansi, labo labaphikisana nekutfola inkhululeko bakhetsa kuvala lencwadzi.
Ngekusho kwe-Catalan authorities, bantfu labangu-1000 balimele emnyakeni lowengcile, ngemuva kwekuzama kwemaphoyisa kutsi aphatamise kuvota etindzaweni tekukhetsa endzaweni lapho bekunebudlova khona.
Emacembu lafuna inkhululeko ahlala endzaweni yekuhlala ngeLesihlanu ntsambama kute avimbele umbhikisho wekusekela emaphoyisa.
Lomkhankhaso wabanjwa, kodvwa kwadzingeka kutsi utsatse luhlangotsi lolwehlukile.
Narcisse Termes, loneminyaka lengu-68 budzala, losebenta nge-electrotechnics, lowaba nencenye emicimbini yekufuna inkhululeko nemkakhe, watsi sewunetintsemba letincane ngelizinga iCatalonia lengatfola ngalo inkhululeko.
"Ngenyanga lephelile, saba nesikhatsi lesimangalisako.
Ngibona batali bami bakhala tinyembeti ngenca yekuvota, kodvwa nyalo simo sesivele siphelile", kwasho yena.
Nanobe baphumelele kakhulu elukhetfweni lwasekhaya lwangaDisemba, emacembu emaCatalan lafuna inkhululeko alwela kugcina emandla awo kulomnyaka, kantsi baholi bawo labanyenti labatiwako sebavele batihambele bona nobe baboshiwe balindzele kuhlolwa ngenca yendzima yabo ekuhleleni lencwadzi yekuhlola kanye nekumemetela inkhululeko.
Joan Puts, losaneminyaka lengu-42 budzala, losanemtfombo wetinsimbi, lowabhala ngemakhalekhikhini akhe imibhikisho lebeyitsandza emaphoyisa, watsi lokuchudzelana bekugcizelelwa bosopolitiki bakuleto tinhlangotsi.
"Loku kwenyuka kancane kancane", kwasho yena.
NgaMgcibelo, Oriol Junqueras, lomunye webakhulumi baseCatalan labamfica labavalelwe ejele emnyakeni lowengcile, wamemetela kutsi utawuncuma kuba lilunga le-European Parliament elukhetfweni lwemnyaka lotako.
"Kuncintisana kwami elukhetfweni lwe-European Union yindlela lekahle yekulahla kucindzetelwa kwemagugu etembuso kanye nekucindzetelwa lesikutfole kuhulumende waseSpain", kwasho yena.
