Umdlalo waMenga waletsa Livestone ku-1-0 ku Rangers
Umgomo wekucala waDolly Menga weLivingston wacinisekisa kutsi labadlali bayawina.
Liveington lelihamba phambili limangale ema Rangers ngekunika Steven Gerrard kulahlekelwa kwakhe kwesibili emidlalweni lengu-18 njengemphatsi welicembu le-Ibrocks.
Umdlalo waDolly Menga wenta umehluko njengoba licembu laGary Holt lishintja libanga ne-Hibernian iya endzaweni yesibili.
Licembu laGerard lisengakabi nelincobe kulelichinga lelibitwa ngekutsi yi-off-season, futsi litawubhekana ne-Hearts, lenemaphuzu lasiphohlongo ngeLisontfo lelilandzelako.
Ngaphambi kwalomdlalo, emaRangers abamba iRapid Vienna ku-Europa League ngaLesine.
Livestone, nyalo, seyichubeka nemncintiswano wayo longenako emageyimu lasitfupha, kantsi umceceshi lomkhulu Holt, usengakaze alahlwe ngumdlalo kusukela atsatsa sikhundla saKennie Miller enyangeni lephelile.
Livejon isicedza ematfuba ebantfu labavakashile
Licembu laHolt bekufanele libe sekucaleni kwemdlalo ngaphambi kwekutsi lifike, ngobe ngekushesha kwalo, belibeka emaRangers engotini.
Scott Robinson watsatsa inhloko waphose wafika ngasekugcineni, kodvwa Alan Lithgow wavala umzamo wakhe ngekushayisa inhloko yaCraig Halcett.
Labadlali bebalandzeli bebalungele kuvumela emaRanger kutsi adlale, ngobe bebati kutsi bangabeka ticu kumadlali labamemile.
Kwaba nguloko lokwabangela kutsi kube nencenye lenkhulu.
I-Ranger yehluleka kuvimbela likiliphu, ngako-ke Livingston wavula, Declan Gallagher naRobinson basebenta ndzawonye batfumela ibhola kuMenga, lowatfola lomdlalo futsi wafaka umgoco.
Ngaleso sikhatsi, emaRanger abeneligunya lelikhulu ekutseni angenele ibhola, kodvwa bekangaboni kutsi angangena njani emagcekeni abo, futsi umgadzi weligili Liam Kelly bekangeke abhekane netimo letimatima.
Loluhlelo lwachubeka nasesigabeni sesibili, nanobe Alfredo Morelos akhipha ibhola kuKelly.
Libhola laScott Pittman laphonswa ngemilente ya-Alan McGregor, umgadzi we-Ranger, futsi liphasi laLithgow laphonswa ngemunye umshayi-ncave waseLivingston.
Kwaba nemaphasi lamabili laphindze aniketwa ngemuva kwekucoshwa, ngemuva kwekucoshwa kwaHulkette, kanye neliphoyinti linye lebantfu labamshaya ngesandla.
"Umdlalo Lomuhle" Lovela kuLivingston - Kuhlolwa
Alexander Lamond, we-BBC Scotland, endzaweni lenkhulu lenemidlalo, i-Tony Macarooni Arena
Umphumela lomuhle we-Livingston.
Bonkhe, ngaphandle kwekukhetsa, bebangetulu kwaloko lebekulindzelwe kubo kuloluhambo lwabo lolunyusa umnotfo.
Indlela labadlala ngayo kanye nebuntfu babo abukashintji ngemuva kwekubuyela esimeni lesihle, kepha Holt naye kumele advunyiswe ngekunikela kwakhe ngenshisekelo.
Licembu lakhe belinemaqhawe lamanyenti.
Umholi Halkhet waba mkhulu, wahola libutfo lelisebenta kahle, kantsi Menga yena wagcina Connor Goldson naJoey Worrell bagadze kakhulu kulo lonkhe lelichinga.
Ngakulolunye luhlangotsi, emaRanger bekangakhutsatwa.
Nanobe bebangemachawe esikhatsini lesendlulile, kodvwa bebangakagcini timiso taGarrard.
Umdlalo wabo wekugcina bewungakapheleli - bebakwati kudlula kulabadlali kanye kuphela, futsi loku kusibonakaliso lesikhanyisako kumaRangers, lasebangeni lelisemkhatsini.
Imibono leyehlukene ngekwemukelwa kwa-Erdogan e-Cologne
Simo besisihle ngaMgcibelo (ngoSeptemba 29) ngesikhatsi baholi bemave aseTurkey naseJalimane bahlangana eBerlin.
Bekulilanga lekugcina lekuvakasha kwaMengameli Erdogan eJalimane, lebekuhloswe kutsi abuyisele budlelwane bakhe ne NATO.
Bebaseceleni kwetimphi ngetindzaba letifaka ekhatsi emalungelo eluntfu, inkhululeko yebetindzaba kanye nekujoyina kweTurkey ku-EU.
Erdogan wase uya e-Cologne kute ayewugubha umkhosi lomkhulu wemasjid.
Lelidolobha linemphakatsi lomkhulu wemaTurkey ngaphandle kweTurkey.
Emaphoyisa avimbela sicumbi sebantfu labangu-25.000 kutsi sihlangane embikwemphakatsi, kodvwa labanyenti balabo labamlangatelelako bakhona kusondzela kute babone umengameli wabo.
Emakhulu ebantfu labamelene na-Erdogan - labanyenti babo labaseKurdistan - nabo babakhona, balahla inchubomgomo ya-Erdogan kanye nesincumo sahulumende waseJalimane sekumemukela kulelive.
Kuhlukana kwebantfu labamemile kukhombisa simo lesingavumelani sendvodza lechamuka eTurkey lebitwa ngaletinye tive ngeligcabho kantsi labanye batsi ingumbusi.
Ingoti yemgwaco eDetford: umgibeli wetibhayisikili uyafa ngemuva kwekushayisana nemoto
