Lomgwaco wenteka etinyangeni letimbalwa ngemuva kwesehlakalo lesifanako lapho umshayeli wabulala umgibeli webhayisikili, lowabese uyafa eChilders Street, lokungaba likhilomitha linye kusuka lapho kwenteka khona lomgwaco ngaLesibili.
