Sichwaga Rosa sisongela iPhoenix, Las Vegas neSalt Lake City ngetikhukhula (tindzawo letomile tingazuza)
Kuyinqaba kutsi kube khona kuhlaleka lokugcwele emagagasi e-Arizona, kodvwa kungenteka kutsi kwenteke ekucaleni kweliviki lelitako, njengobe emagagasi laphuma ku-Hurricane Rosa atawugeleta eningizimu-nshonalanga yelihlane, ahambisa tikhukhula.
I-NMS sevele ikhiphe tiphephandzaba tekuvikelwa kwetikhukhula ngeMsombuluko nangoLesibili kusuka eWestern Arizona kuya eSouthern and Eastern Nevada, eSoutheastern California kanye nase Utah, kufaka ekhatsi iPhoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas kanye neSalt Lake City.
Sichwaga Rosa silindzelwe kutsi sidzabule sifike edvute nePhoenix ngaLesibili, lapho sitawufika khona ngeMsombuluko.
I-Phoenix National Weather Service yatfumela umbiko ku-twitter yatsi: "Kube netiphepho letingu-10 letisolo tihlala tivikelekile noma tibe ngaphansi kwemakhilomitha langu-200 kusuka ePhoenix kusukela nga-1950!
Katrina (1967) bekusiphepho lesingasekho ngemamayela langu-40 kusuka emnyeleni wase-Arizona".
I-National Hurricane Center yabika kutsi kutawuba nemvula lenkhulu lengemamitha lamabili kuya kulamane, kantsi kuletinye tindzawo kutawuba nemvula lenemamitha lasitfupha eMongolian Rim, e-Arizona.
Letinye tindzawo letiseNingizimu-nshonalanga ye-United States, kufaka ekhatsi i-Central Rocky Mountains ne-Great Basin, kungenteka kutsi tibe nemvula lenemamitha la-1 kuya ku-2 ngemvula, kantsi letinye tingaba nemamitha la-4 ngemvula.
Etindzaweni letingenasifo setikhukhula, imvula leletfwa nguRosa ingaba sibusiso, ngobe lendzawo iyahlupheka ngenca yesomiso.
Nanobe tikhukhula tiyingoti, lokunye kwalomvula lokubangelwa nguwo kutawuba lusito, njengobe emave laseNingizimu-nshonalanga ahlangabetana nesomiso.
Ngekusho kwe-U.S. Drought Monitor, ngetulu kwa-40% we-Arizona unetindzawo letinemvula leningi, lokuyindzawo yesibili lenemvula leningi", kusho i-weather.com.
Kwekucala, Sichwaga Rosa sitawufika eMexico leseBacha California.
Njengobe lesiphepho sichubeka sivutsela, ngeLisontfo ekuseni iRosa itawuba ngemakhilomitha langu-385 eningizimu yePunta Eugenia, eMexico, futsi itawuba nemoya lomkhulu longemakhilomitha langu-85 ngeli-awa futsi itawuhamba ngesivinini lesingu-12 ngeli-awa.
Lesiphepho sitawuhlangana nemanti labandzako ase Pacific, ngako-ke sitawucina.
Ngako-ke, kulindzeleke kutsi lifike eMexico njengelivungu lesivunguvungu ngeLisontfo ntsambama nobe ebusuku.
Kutawuna kakhulu etincenyeni taseMexico, lokungabangela kutsi kube netikhukhula letinyenti.
"Kutawuba nemvula lenkhulu lengaba ngemasentimitha lamatsatfu kuya kulasitfupha kusuka eBaha California kuya eSonora lese nyakatfo-nshonalanga, lengaba ngemasentimitha lalishumi", kusho i-weather.com.
Ngemuva kwaloko, iRosa itawuya enyakatfo itewufika eMexico njengesichwaga futsi itawufika e-Arizona ekuseni ngeLesibili njengesichwaga lesincane lesisezingeni lelisetulu, bese idzabula i-Arizona ite ifinyelele eningizimu ye-Utah ngeLesibili kusihlwa.
"Ingoti lenkhulu lebukene neSiphepho Rosa nobe tinsalela taso, kuba nemvula lenkhulu kakhulu eBaja California, enyakatfo-nshonalanga yeSonora kanye naseNingizimu-nshonalanga yeMelika", kusho i-National Hurricane Center.
