Trump utsi Kavanaugh "waphila ngaphansi kwelulaka nenzondo" yelicembu lemaDemocrats.
"Kuvotelwa kweMehluleli Kavanaugh kusho kutsi awusayifuni indlela lenelunya naletfukutsele yelicembu lemaDemocrats", kwasho Trump emhlanganweni lobewuse Wheeling, eWest Virginia.
Trump watsi Kavanaugh "wabhekana nelulaka nenzondo" yelicembu lemaDemocrats ngesikhatsi sekukhetfwa kwakhe.
Kavanaugh wafakaza embikweSigungu saVelonkhe ngeLesihlanu, waphika ngalokuphelele nangendlela lebonakalako kutsi uyavumelana netinsolo taChristine Blaisey Ford tekutsi wamhlukubeta ngekwelicasi eminyakeni leminyenti leyendlulile ngesikhatsi basengakefiki eminyakeni yekutfomba.
Ford waphindze wafakaza enkantolo mayelana naletimangalo takhe.
Lomengameli watsi ngaLesibili "bantfu baseMelika babone bukhulu, lizinga kanye nesibindzi" saKavanaugh ngalelo langa.
"Livoti lekucinisekisa kubekwa kwaSomajaji Kavanaugh lisincumo sekucinisekisa lomunye wetingcondvo temtsetfo letiphumelelako esikhatsini setfu, ummeli lonemlandvo lomuhle wekusebentela sive", watjela linyenti lebantfu lebebamlalele eWest Virginia.
Umengameli wakhuluma ngekungakhetsi ngekuncuma kwaCavanaugh, ngesikhatsi akhuluma ngekubaluleka kwekubamba lichaza kwe-Republican kulolukhetfo lolutawuba semkhatsini.
"Sisekhatsi nemaviki lasihlanu solo singakayivotela leminye yemikhankaso lebalulekile emphilweni yetfu.
Angisiye umlingani, kepha empeleni nginguye", kwasho yena.
"Ngako-ke ngiya emaveni lamanyenti ngisekela bantfu labatsite labakahle".
