Kuhlaselwa lokukhulu lokwentiwa kutamatama kwemhlaba kanye ne-tsunami e-Indonesia, kubangele kutsi bantfu labanyenti bafe.
Lokungenani bantfu labangu-384 babulawa, labanyenti babo badvonswa ngemagagasi lamakhulu labengeletwe lwandle ngesikhatsi kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kanye ne-tsunami kubhubhisa sihlenge sase-Indonesia, i-Sulawesi, tiphatsimandla tatsi ngeLisontfo.
Emakhulu ebantfu abegcwele elugwini lwasePalu ngaLesihlanu, ngesikhatsi emagagasi lamakhulu lasitfupha ema-sentimitha lamakhulu, ahamba acondze elugwini, ahudvula bantfu labanyenti, futsi abhubhisa konkhe lokwakusendleleni yawo.
Le tsunami yavela ngemuva kwekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokungu-7.5.
"Ngesikhatsi kusongela kwe-tsunami kubikwa, bantfu bebaselugwini futsi abazange bagijime masinyane, ngako-ke batsintseka", kusho Sudopo Purwo Nugroho, lokhulumela i-BNPB, e-Indonesia, etfuleni leliphefumulelwe eJakarta.
"Letsunami ayizange ize, yashayela imoto, imitsi, tindlu, yashaya konkhe emhlabatsini", kwasho Nguyenroho, wengeta ngekutsi itsunami yahamba emantini ngejubane lelingemakhilomitha la-800 ngelihora ngaphambi kwekutsi ishaye.
Watsi labanye bantfu bebakwati kugibela tihlahla kute babalekele lomonakalo futsi basindza.
Bantfu labangu-16,700 batfunyelwa etindzaweni letingu-24 ePalu.
Titfombe letishicilelwe nguhulumende wetehlakalo tibonisa tindlu letinyenti letibhidlikile kanye netitolo, emabhuloho labhidlikile kanye nelithempeli lelisemantini.
Kutamatama kwemhlaba kwachubeka nekushaya lelidolobha leliselwandle ngeMgcibelo.
Loku kwenteka endzaweni lenebantfu labangu-2,4 wetigidzi.
I-BPPT yase-Indonesia, itsi emandla lakhululwa ngekutamatama kwemhlaba lokwenteka ngaLesihlanu, abengacishe abe ngemakhulu lamabili emahlandla lamakhulu emandla ebhomu le-athomu lelahlaselwa eHiroshima eMphini Yelive Yesibili.
Watsi: "Lendzawo lephakeme yaseTsunami, lesekugcineni kweligede lelidvutane, ingenta kutsi lomfula ube mkhulu kakhulu".
Ngroho wachaza lomonakalo ngekutsi "ngumonakalo lomkhulu" waphindze watsi emakhaya lamakhulu, tibhedlela, tindzawo tekutsengisela kanye nemahhotela kwabhidlika.
Watsi tinombolo tetinhlupheko tatitfola tivalelwe ngaphansi kwemabhodo etakhiwo letishayako, kwatsi bantfu labangu-540 balimala kantsi labangu-29 basengakalindzeli.
Ngroho watsi kubulawa nekulimala kungenteka kube kukhulu elugwini lolungemakhilomitha langu-300 enyakatfo yePalu, endzaweni lebitwa ngekutsi yiDongala, lesedvute nendzawo yekuhlaselwa.
Tindlela tekuchumana "tiphelile futsi kute lwati" lolutfolakale eDongola, watsi.
"Bantfu labangetulu kwa-300 000 bahlala khona", kusho iRed Cross esitatimendeni sayo, yatsi tisebenti tayo kanye nemavolontiya ayachubeka aya etindzaweni letitsintsekile.
"Loku sekuyindzaba lenkhulu futsi ingase ibe yimbi kakhulu", kwasho yena.
