Lee wabona kubaluleka kwemincintiswano leyengcile yelucwaningo lwebuchwepheshe yeHulumende waseMelika, lefana neDARPA Robotics Challenge, wabuta kutsi lolokulandzelako kutawugcwaliswa nini kute kubonakale labantfu labatawufuna kwenta lolokunye.
