"Lwandle lwangakitsi": EmaBolivia labhaceliwe anethemba lekutsi inkantolo itawuvula indlela leya ePasifiki
Emaphoyisa asebenta emgodzini lonemathuluzi ekuvikela ema-air force eLa Paz.
Emagumbi ahulumende anetimphahla letiluhlata sasibhakabhaka.
Emakhoseni etfu aselwandle, kusukela eLake Titicaca kuya e-Amazon, kunemlayeto lotsi: "Lwandle lwami ngelikhwa.
Kungumsebenti wetfu kuwutfola".
Kuyo yonkhe indzawo lese Bolivia, kukhunjulwa kwelugede lolwaluniketwe live lase Chile ngemuva kwekulwa kamatima ngeminyaka yabo-1900, kusolo kusagcwele, kanye nesifiso sebantfu bakhona sekuhamba bayewubona iPacific Ocean.
Lamatsemba avuswe kakhulu nyalo kunakucala emashumini eminyaka, njengobe iBolivia ilindzele sincumo seNkantolo yeMave Emhlaba ngeLusuku lwekucala lwanga-October ngemuva kweminyaka lesihlanu yekubonisana.
"IBolivia inemoya wekuthula, wekubumbana, futsi ngekwemvelo ilindzele umphumela wayo ngekuciniseka", kwasho Roberto Calzantela, longumdiplomate waseBolivia.
Bantfu labanyenti baseBolivia batawubuka sincumo seNkantolo yeMave Emhlaba (i-ICJ) kumabonakudze lamakhulu kulo lonkhe live, banematsemba ekutsi inkantolo yase-The Hague itawutsatsa sincumo lesivumelana ne-Bolivia kutsi ibe ne-Chile, ngemuva kwemashumi eminyaka yetingcoco letichubekako, kutsi icocisane ngekuniketwa kwe-Bolivia indlela leyinkhulu yekungena elwandle.
Evo Morales, umengameli waseBolivia lonelwati lolunyenti, lotawuvota kulolubito lolutawuvuselelwa kulomnyaka lotako, unalokunyenti langakwenta nobe langakulahlekelwa kuko ngesincumo semcimbi weMsombuluko.
"Sisondzele kakhulu ekutseni sibuyele ePacific", wetsembisa ekupheleni kwa-Agasti.
Nanobe kunjalo, labanye bahloli bakholelwa kutsi leNkantolo angeke ivume kutsi iBolivia iyemukela, futsi ngisho nobe beyingavuma, bekungeke kube netingucuko letinkhulu.
Lesikhungo se-UN eNetherlands asinalo ligunya lekuniketa emave langema-thousand futsi sichazile kutsi angeke sicinisekise imiphumela yetinkhulumo letingaba khona.
Lokutsi sincumo seNkantolo yeMave Emhlaba sitawukhishwa ngemuva kwetinyanga letisitfupha setfulwe emacala ekugcina, kukhombisa kutsi lendzaba "beyingekho matima", kusho Paza Zarate, losati semtsetfo wemave emhlaba waseChile.
Esikhundleni sekutsi isite kakhulu ekufezeni tinhloso teBolivia, leminyaka lemine leyengcile ingahle ibe yimbi kakhulu.
"Hulumende waseBolivia nyalo sewutitsatsele yena lendzaba yekufinyelela elwandle", kusho Zarate.
Watsi inkhulumo lehlaselako yaMorales isuse tonkhe tifiso letinhle taseChile.
I-Bolivia ne-Chile batawuchubeka bakhulume ngalesinye sikhatsi, kodvwa kutawuba matima kakhulu kutsi kube netingcoco ngemuva kwaloko.
Lamave lamabili akakasebentisani ngemancusa kusukela nga-1962.
Lomunye ummeleli waseBolivia e-The Hague, lobekanguMengameli wangaphambilini Eduardo Rodriguez Velze, wawala umbono wekutsi lenchubo yekukhipha sincumo seNkantolo beyiphutfuma kakhulu.
NgeMsombuluko, iBolivia itawutfola "litfuba lelihle lekuvula sikhatsi lesisha ebudlelwaneni bayo neChile" kanye nelitfuba "lekucedza timphi teminyaka lengu-139 letisebenta ngekubambisana", kwasho yena.
Calzantela waphindze waphika kutsi Morales, losolo angumholi lotsandvwa kakhulu e-Latin America, usebentisa lendzaba yekuphuma uye elwandle njengentfo leyenta bantfu bangaboni.
"IBolivia angeke ililahle lilungelo layo lekufinyelela eLwandle lwePacific", kwengeta yena.
