John Edward: Emakhono elulwimi ayadzingeka kubantfu bemhlaba.
Tikolwa letizimele taseScotland tinemlandvo wekuphumelela kahle emfundvweni, lokuchubekile nga 2018, ngekuphumelela lokukhulu etihlolweni, lokuvele kuciniswe ngetinzuzo temuntfu ngamunye kanye netinzuzo temphakatsi kutemidlalo, tebuciko, temculo kanye naleminye imisebenti yemphakatsi.
Ngalabafundzi labangetulu kwa-30 000 eScotland, letikolo, letimelwe yi Scottish Council of Independent Schools (SCIS), tihlose kuniketa bafundzi nebatali babo tinsita letincono kakhulu.
Imfundvo letimele ihlose kucecesha bafundzi kutsi batfole tifundvo letinyenti, bakwati kufundza imisebenti leyehlukahlukene kanye nekutfola sikhundla sekuba takhamuti temhlaba.
Njengemkhakha wemfundvo longahle ukhone kwakha nekwenta luhlelo lwemfundvo yesikolo loluhlelwe ngendlela, sibona kutsi tilwimi tesimanje tihlala tiyimfundvo leyemukelekako futsi lefunwako etikolweni.
Nelson Mandela watsi: "Nawukhuluma nemuntfu ngelulwimi lalucondzako, loko lokushoko kungena engcondvweni yakhe.
Nangabe ukhuluma naye ngelulwimi lwakhe, loko lokushoko kuya enhlitiyweni yakhe".
Loku kusikhumbuta kutsi singete sasitsembela esiNgisini kuphela uma sifuna kwakha budlelwane nekwetsembana nebantfu bakulamanye emave.
Ngeticu temnyaka, tilwimi tibekwe ngetulu kwetinombolo tekuphumelela, ngetinombolo letiphakeme kakhulu etikolweni letitimele.
Bonkhe bafundzi labangu-68 ekhulwini labafundza tilwimi tangaphandle batfole ticu te-A.
Umniningwane lovela etikolweni letingu-74 letililunga le-SCIS ukhombisa kutsi bafundzi labangu-72 ekhulwini batfole ticu letiphakeme tesiMandarin, kantsi labangu-72 ekhulwini labafundza siJalimane, labangu-69 ekhulwini labafundza siFulentji, kanye nalabangu-63 ekhulwini labafundza siSpanish nabo batfole ticu letiphakeme.
Loku kukhombisa kutsi tikolwa letitimele eScotland tikhutsata kusetjentiswa kwetilwimi tesilumbi njengelulwimi lolubalulekile lolutawusetjentiswa bantfwana kanye nebantfu labasha esikhatsini lesitako.
Tilwimi njengetifundvo letikhetsiwe lamuhla, tibhekwa njengaletibalulekile njengaleti letiphatselene nesayensi, iteknoloji, bunjiniyela netibalo eluhlelweni lwetemfundvo etikolweni letitimele nakuletinye tindzawo.
Luhlolo lweKhomishani yeTemisebenti nemaKhono yanga-2014 lwembula kutsi, ngetizatfu tekutsi kungani bacashi bakutfola kumatima kugcwalisa tikhala temisebenti, emaphesenti langu-17 abhekiswe ekungakhoni kusebentisa lulwimi.
Ngaloko-ke, sidzingo sekutfola emakhono elulwimi siya ngekuya sikhula kute bantfu labasha balungele umsebenti wabo esikhatsini lesitako.
Njengobe ematfuba emsebenti lamanyenti esikhatsini lesitako adzinga lwati lwetilwimi, lamakhono abalulekile eveni leligcwele kubumbana.
Ngisho nobe ungakhetsa ngumuphi umsebenti, kufundza lulwimi lwesibili kutawuba lusito lolukhulu kuwe esikhatsini lesitako, ngobe kutawuba lusito lolutawusebenta kuphila kwakho konkhe.
Nangabe umuntfu akwati kuchumana nebantfu bakulamanye emave ngalokucondzile, lomuntfu lofundza tilwimi letinyenti utawuba nenzuzo lenkhulu kunalomncintiswano.
Ngekusho kweluphenyo lwe-YouGov lwebantfu labadzala labangetulu kwa-4 000 e-UK nga-2013, emaphesenti langu-75 alabo labaphendvulwe abakwati kukhuluma lulwimi lwakulelinye live kahle ngalokwenele kutsi bakhulume, kantsi siFulentshi bekusilo lulwimi kuphela lolukhulunywa yinombolo lephindvwe kabili kubantfu labaphendvulwe (emaphesenti langu-15).
Kungako-ke, kutsenga imali ekufundziseni tilwimi kubalulekile kubantfwana balamuhla.
Kwati tilwimi letinyenti, ikakhulukati tilwimi letisemnotfweni lotfutfukako, kutawuniketa bantfwana ematfuba lamanyenti ekutfola umsebenti lonenjongo.
EScotland, tonkhe tikolwa titawufundzisa tilwimi letehlukene.
Letinye tikolwa titawufundzisa ngetilwimi letisemtsetfweni, kantsi letinye titawufundzisa ngetilwimi letibaluleke kakhulu e-UK letitawubakhona nga-2020, njengesiMandarin noma siJapane.
Nobe ngabe yini umntfwana wakho layitsandzako, kutawuba khona tilwimi langakhetsa kuto etikolweni letitimele, lapho khona banelwati loluphelele lwetifundvo.
Tikolwa teScotland letitimele tiyatinikela ekufundziseni bantfwana ngendlela letabenta balungele kufundza futsi tibanike emakhono labadzingako kute baphumelele, nobe ngabe yini letawenteka esikhatsini lesitako.
