Umhlangano waTrump eWest Virginia, YouTube Channel
Mengameli Donald Trump ucala luhlelo lwemhlangano wekucala eWilling, eWest Virginia.
Loku kungumhlangano wekucala kuleminye lemihlanu Trump lafuna kuyenta kuleliviki lelitako, lokufaka ekhatsi kuvakasha etindzaweni letisedvute, letifaka ekhatsi iTennessee neMississippi.
Njengobe sekusele livoti lekucinisekisa kutsi sewukhetsiwe kutsi abe nguSomajaji, Trump ufuna kutfutfukisa kwesekelwa kwebantfu elukhetfweni lolutawucala, njengoba emaRiphabhulikhi angahle alahlekelwe kulawula kweSigungu saVelonkhe ngekukhetsa lokwenteka ngaNovemba.
Ngusiphi sikhatsi semhlangano waTrump eWest Virginia lamuhla ntsambama, futsi ungakubukela njani ku-inthanethi?
Umhlangano waTrump eWilling, eWest Virginia, uhlelelwe kutsi ube nga-7 ebusuku kusihlwa ngeMgcibelo, September 29, 2018.
Ungakhona kubukela umhlangano waTrump eWest Virginia ku-YouTube.
Trump kungenteka akhulume ngetimphikiswano talokungenwa nguBret Kavanaugh, lotawuba lijaji leNkantolo lePhakeme kulelive, letenteke ngesizatfu sekusolwa kwebugebengu lobutsite lobutsite lobutsite, kanye nevoti yekucinisekisa le-Senate lebeseyime liviki linye ngesikhatsi luphenyo lwe-FBI lusolo lusendleleni.
Nanobe kunjalo, inhloso lenkhulu yaloluhlelo lwekuhlangana, kusita emaRiphabhulikhi labukene nekuphuma kwetinkhululeko ngaNovemba kute atfole emandla.
Ngako-ke, umholi welicembu lemkhankaso waMengameli Trump utsi lemibutsano lesihlanu lelandzelako ivamise kuhloswa ngayo "kucinisa emavolontiya kanye nebasekeli njengoba emaRiphabliki etama kuvikela kanye nekukhulisa emavoti abo esiGungwini seMalunga kanye neSigungu seTikhulu", kusho iReuters.
"Kuhlola liKhabhinethi kubalulekile eluhlelweni lwakhe, umengameli uya emaveni lamanyenti njengobe sesingene esikhatsini sekukhankasela", kusho sikhulumi semkhankaso waTrump lesingafuni kukhulunyelwa ngelibito.
Umhlangano lohlelelwe kusihlwa eWilling's Wesbanco Arena, ungaletsa basekeli "basesifundzeni sase-Ohio nase-Pennsylvania, futsi ungaletsa kwatiswa lokunyenti lokutfolakala etindzabeni temsakato wasePittsburgh", kusho i-West Virginia Metro News.
NgaMgcibelo, kutawuba kwesibili enyangeni kutsi Trump avakashele eWest Virginia, live laphindze lawina ngemaphesenti langetulu kwa-40 nga-2016.
Trump wetama kusita Patrick Morrissey, umlingani we-Republican wase-West Virginia kutsi abe ngumengameli, lobekahlele phansi kakhulu.
"Akusilo liphuzu lelihle kuMorrissey kutsi umengameli kumele ete atame kumkhutsata kutsi akhetse", kusho Simon Hender, losati setembusave eNyuvesi yaseWest Virginia, ngekusho kwe-Reuters.
