Umdlalo wekushaya emabhokisi ngukona kuyincenye yemidlalo, kodvwa badlali batsatsa lomdlalo njengentfo lebalulekile, ikakhulukati kuletindzawo letibanti.
Bebatawutsi usiphi sikhatsi nyalo?
"Bekungemakhasi lasitfupha ngaphambili, manje sekungemakhasi lamane, ngako-ke kungenteka kutsi sesinelitfuba lelincane", kwasho Jordan Speith nakaphuma emini.
I-Europe inelitsemba, yebo, lekuhola ngemaphuzu lamane bese kusele emaphuzu langu-12 emdlalweni.
Bantfu baseMelika, njengobe Spith asho, banemoya lomuhle, futsi banalokunyenti lokungabakhutsata, njengemajaha lamabili lafana naSpith naJustin Thomas labadlala ndzawonye lilanga lonkhe futsi ngamunye wabo watfola emaphuzu lamatsatfu kulena lemine.
