I-Europe itsatsa embili 10-6 ngelilanga lekugcina le-Ryder Cup
I-Europe itawuba nelikhono lelikhulu ngelilanga lekugcina le-Ryder Cup ngemuva kwekucinisa ema-fourball kanye nema-foursomes ngeMgcibelo nga-10-6 kuma-USA.
Umlingani lowakhutsatako waTommy Fleetwood naFrancesco Molinari, wacala ngekuncoba kabili umlingani wakhe Tiger Woods, waphindze waphumelela kuhola umncintiswano weLe Golf National ngemaphuzu lamane.
Licembu laseYurophu laThomas Bjorn, lebelifuna kugcina indondo lebeyilahlekile eHazeltine eminyakeni lemibili leyendlulile, lacedza licembu laseMelika lebeliphambene, ngemdlalo wemagoli lamatsatfu kuya kulalishumi ekuseni.
I-USA yabamba umzabalazo lomkhulu, yawina imicimbi lemibili, kepha yehluleka kuvala umehluko.
Licembu laJim Furyk lidzinga emaphuzu lasiphohlongo kulamashumi lamabili nakune emdlalweni welibhola letinyawo ngeLisontfo kute lihlale lineligoli.
Fleetwood nguye umdlali wekucala waseYurophu lowatfola emaphuzu lamane emncintiswaneni, kantsi yena kanye na Molinari, lowatiwa ngekutsi "nguMollywood", ngemuva kwemphelasontfo lomuhle, baba ngemabili kuphela labane emaphuzu lamane emidlalweni lemine yekucala emlandvweni weRyder Cup.
Ngemuva kwekubhubhisa boWoods naPatrick Reid kuma-fourball, bahlangana ndzawonye kute bacedze iWoods lephelelwe ngemandla kanye ne-American Bryson Desambo ngemdlalo lomkhulu we-5&4.
Woods, lowabamba imicimbi lemibili ngaLesibili, wakhombisa kuqhuma kwesikhashana, kepha sewulahlekelwe yimidlalo yakhe lengemashumi layimfica nakunye kulengu-29 ku-fourball naku-foursome kanye naku-series.
Justin Rose, lowephuta emini emdlalweni we-fourball, wabuyela ku-foursome yakhe Henry Stenson ngekuhlaselwa ngu Dustin Johnson na Brooks Keppa nga-2 na-1, batfola indzawo yekucala kanye nalesihlanu emhlabeni.
Kute lokuhle lokwenteka eYurophu ngaphandle kwelilanga lelihle lelipholile eningizimu-nshonalanga yeParis.
Umpetfu wemidlalo lemitsatfu, Jordan Spieth kanye naJustin Thomas, babeka lizinga le-American League ngemaphuzu lamabili ngeMgcibelo.
Baphuma baphumelela 2&1 ku John Ram kanye na Ian Poulter base Spain ku fourball base babuya emuva kuncoba Poulter na Rory McIlroy ku 4&3 ku foursome kantsi bebahluleke kugcina emagoli lamabili ekuvula.
