INyakatho Korea itsi angeke ikhiphe tikhali yayo ngaphandle kwekucinisekisa kutsi iyachubeka nekusebenta
INdvuna Yetepolitiki yaseNyakatfo Korea yatsi kuUN Saturday kutsi kucindzetelwa kwetintfo letitsite kukhulisa kungetsembi kweMelika nekutsi live layo ngeke liyekele tikhali talo te-nuclear ngalokuphelele.
Ri Yong Ho watjela umhlangano wemnyaka we-UNWTO kutsi iNorth Korea itsetse "tinyatselo letibalulekile tekutitsandzela" kulomnyaka lowengcile, njengekumisa luhlolo lwentfutfu yeluhlavu lwemphi, luhlolo lwentfutfu yemphi, kanye nekwenta sivumelwano sekungasakatwa kwetikhali te-nuclear kanye ne-nuclear technology.
"Noko, asikaboni kuphendvula lokunjalo kusuka eMelika", kwasho yena.
"Ngaphandle kwekwetsembela eMelika, kute kwetsembela kuvikeleka kwetfu, futsi ngaphansi kwaletimo kute indlela yekucala ngekwehlukana kwetfu".
Ngesikhatsi Ri aphindze aveta kukhonona lokwatiko kwe North Korea mayelana nekumelana kwe Washington 'nekuchubekela' ekucedzeni kukhulula, lokusho kutsi iNorth Korea itawuvuzwa njengoba ichubeka nalenchubo, sitatimende sakhe besibalulekile ngekutsi akazange akuvimbele ngalokuphelele kukhulula ngekungakhetsi, njengobe Pyongyang yente esikhatsini lesengcile.
Ri ukhuluma ngesimemetelo lesisembili lesashiwo nguKim Jong Un naDonald Trump emhlanganweni wekucala wemengameli waseMelika kanye nemholi waseNyakatfo Korea eSingapore ngaJuni 12, lapho Kim atsembisa kusebentela "kucedza kusebentisa i-nuclear ye-Korean Peninsula", kantsi Trump wetsembisa kucinisekisa kuphepha kwe-North Korea.
INyakatfo Korea ifuna kucedza imphi yaseKorea yanga-1950-53, kodvwa iMelika itsi iPyongyang kufanele "inikele" tikhali tayo te-nuclear kucala.
I-Washington iphindze yabhekana netimemo tekunciphisa tikhalo letimatima temave emhlaba letibekwe i-North Korea.
"IMelika icindzetela kutsi 'kucedvwe' i-nuclear, futsi ikhulisa umfutfo ngekusongela ngekuhlawuliswa kwentela kufeza inhloso yayo ngekubamba ngenkhani, kubeka ematfuba ekutsi 'kucedvwe' imphi", kusho Ri.
"Lokucabanga kutsi tijeziso tingasibeka etinyaweni, liphupho lalabo labangati.
Kodvwa inkinga kutsi kucindzetelwa lokuchubekako kucinisa kungetsembi kwetfu".
Ri akazange akhulume ngenkomfa yesibili lebeyihlelwe emkhatsini waKim naTrump, lokunguyona leyashiwo ngumengameli waseMelika kuUN earlier this week.
Kodvwa-ke, lomkhulumeli waveta kuhlangana lokutsatfu emkhatsini waKim kanye nemholi waseNingizimu Korea Moon Jae-in etinyangeni letisihlanu letengcile, watsi: "Kube i-South Korea beyiyindzawo yekuhlanta i-nuclear hhayi i-United States, kuthula kwe-nuclear yase-Korea bekungeke kube yintfo lematima kangaka".
Noma kunjalo, indlela labekhuluma ngayo beyehluke kakhulu kuloko labekusho emhlanganweni we-UN ngemnyaka lowengcile, nakatsi kuhlasela live laseMelika ngemakhemikhali aseNyakatfo Korea bekungeke kugwenywe ngobe "Mengameli loMbi" Trump abetsi Kim "ngumuntfu lonemphi" lotawutibulala.
Kulomnyaka, e-UN, Trump, lowetsembisa "kubhubhisa" iNyakatfo Korea, wancoma Kim ngekutfukutsela kwakhe ekuchubeni netinyatselo tekucedza tikhali, kepha watsi kunyenti lokusamele kwentiwe nekutsi tijeziso kumele tihlale tisekhona kute iNyakatfo Korea icedze tikhali.
NgaLwesitsatfu, Trump watsi kute sikhatsi latawusicitsa, watsi: "Nangabe kutsatsa iminyaka lemibili, iminyaka lemitsatfu nobe tinyanga letisihlanu, akukhatsaliseki".
