Bafundzi baseHarvard bafundza tifundvo tekutsi bangaphumula kahle njani
Kulomnyaka, lucwaningo lolusha lwaseHarvard University luhlose kutsi bonkhe bafundzi labasebancane balale sikhatsi lesidze etinyatselweni tekulwa nemasiko lakhulako ekufundza ebusuku kakhulu kanye nekudla kakhulu i-caffeine.
Lesinye sati semfundvo satfola kutsi bafundzi basenyuvesi lenkhulu emhlabeni wonkhe bavame kungati tintfo letisisekelo, njengekutsi bangativikela njani.
Charles T. Chiessler, longuphrofesa weTemphilo yeTemphilo yaseHarvard, kanye nelusito lwetemphilo eBrigham and Women's Hospital, waklama lesifundvo, labakholelwa kutsi singesekucala eMelika.
Watfola sikhutsato sekufundzisa ngemuva kwekwetfula inkhulumo lemayelana nemiphumela yekungalali kahle ekufundzeni.
"Ekugcineni, kwefika intfombatana yatsi: "Kungani ngifundza ngalendzaba nyalo nje, emnyakeni wami wekugcina?"
Watsi kute umuntfu lowake wakhuluma naye ngekubaluleka kwekulala - lokwangimangalisa", watjela i-Telegraph.
Lesifundvo, lesisandza kucala kulomnyaka, sifundzisa bafundzi timiso letisisekelo tekutsi imikhuba lemihle yekulala ibaluleke kangakanani ekuchubeni kahle esikolweni nasemidlalweni, kanye nasekwenteni ncono imphilo yemuntfu.
Paul Barreira, longumfundzisi wetemphilo yengcondvo eHarvard Medical School kanye nemcondzisi lomkhulu wetemphilo kuleyunivesithi, watsi leyunivesithi yancuma kufaka lesifundvo ngesikhatsi itfola kutsi bafundzi bebangakhoni kulala kahle ngeliviki.
Lesikolwa lesitsatsa ema-awa langu-10, sihlanganisa umsebenti lotsite wekuhlanganyela.
Kulenye incenye, kunesitfombe sendzawo yekulala yebafundzi, lapho bafundzi bacofa khona tinkomishi tenkhomishi, emakhethini, ticatfulo temidlalo kanye netincwadzi, kute batfole lwati ngemiphumela yekunatsa kakhulu ikhofi kanye nekukhanya, kutsi kusebenta kahle kwemidlalo kutsintseka njani ngekungakhoni kulala kahle, kanye nekubaluleka kwekulala kahle.
Kulomunye umculu, labantfu bafundza ngekutsi kulahlekelwa butfongo sikhatsi lesidze kungakhulisa njani ingoti yekushaywa yinhlitiyo, sifo semsheko, kucindzeteleka kanye nemdlavuza.
I-campus map lenetitfombe letiveta kuhlangana, ikhutsata labadlala kuleyo midlalo kutsi bacabange ngemisebenti yabo yemalanga onkhe.
"Siyati kutsi angeke kusishintje ngalokucondzile simo sebantfu labafundza kuletikolwa.
Kodvwa-ke, sicabanga kutsi banalo lilungelo lekwati, njengobe nawe unalo lilungelo lekwati ngetingoti tekuphila nangabe ukhetsa kubhema", kwengeta Phrofesa Chiessler.
Watsi: "Lisiko lekutigcabha ngekutsi ufundze busuku bonkhe lisekhona, futsi iteknoloji yakamuva kanye nekucindzeteleka kwebafundzi kukwenta kube matima kakhulu kutsi ulale kahle".
Watsi, kulala kahle kufanele kube "sikhali semfihlo" sebafundzi kute balwe nekucindzeteleka, kuphelelwa ngemandla kanye nekwesaba, ngisho nekugwema kukhuluphala, ngobe kungakhoni kulala kahle kubeka ingcondvo endzaweni yekungakhoni kudla, lokwenta umuntfu ahlale ativa alambile.
Raymond Shaw, umfundzi loneminyaka lengu-19 losuka eCalifornia lofundza ngekhemistri kanye nemvelo, wasita phrofesa Cheisler ekuhleleni lesifundvo, njengobe bekafundzele sifundvo sakhe emnyakeni wakhe wekucala eHarvard.
