HIV/Aids: I-China ibika kukhula lokungu-14% etinhluphekweni letinsha
I-China imemetele kukhula lokungu-14% kwebantfu labane-HIV ne-AIDS.
Bantfu labangetulu kwa-820 000 kulelive bayatsintseka, ngekusho kwetikhungo tetemphilo.
NgeNkhwekhweti yesiBili ya-2018 kuphela, kwabika emacala lamasha la-40 000.
Kubo labanyenti, lamacala lamasha atfolakala ngekuhlanganyela ngekwelicansi, lokusho kutsi kunesimo lesishintjile endvulo.
Ngekwesintfu, ligciwane le-HIV beliyandza kakhulu etindzaweni letitsite eChina ngenca yekumpontjelwa ingati lengenalesifo.
Nanobe kunjalo, linani lebantfu labangenwa yi-HIV ngalendlela seliphelile, njengobe kwasho tiphatsimandla tetemphilo eChina emhlanganweni lobewuse Yunnan.
Nanobe kunjalo, nangabe kucatsaniswa nemnyaka lowengcile, linani lebantfu labane-HIV ne-AIDS eChina lenyuke ngemakhulu lalikhulu.
Kudluliselwa kwe-HIV ngekwelicasi kuyinkinga lenkhulu emmangweni wema-LGBT eChina.
Lobufanani lobungatsatfwa njengentfo lebulelekile eChina nga-1997, kodvwa lubandlululo lolwentiwa kubantfu labangephandle kweLGBT lusolo lugcwele.
Ngenca yemagugu lacondzile alelive, lucwaningo lukhomba kutsi emadvodza langaba ngu-70 kuya ku-90 ekhulwini lalala nemadvodza atawugcine ashade nalabasikati.
Tinyenti tifo letitsatselwanako letibangelwa kungakhoni kuvikela kahle ngekwelicasi kuleto tihlobo.
Kusukela nga-2003, hulumende waseChina wetsembise kufinyelela jikelele kumitsi lelapha iHIV, njengencenye yekulwa naloludzaba.
