I-US ingasebentisa emaNavy ayo 'kuvala' ngekubamba lokutfunyelwa ngaphandle kwemandla eRussia - INdvuna Yetelitiko Letasekhaya
I-Washington ingasebentisa ema-Navy ayo "uma kudzingeka" kute ivimbele kutsi emandla aseRussia angafakwa etimakethe, kufaka ekhatsi iMiddle East, kusho umBhalisi weLitiko Letasekhaya laseMelika, Ryan Zinke, ngekusho kwe-Washington Examiner.
Zindzi washo kutsi kungenela kweRussia eSyria, lapho isebenta khona ngekucelwa nguhulumende losemtsetfweni, kuyindlela yekufuna emakethe lensha yemandla.
"Ngicabanga kutsi tizatfu letibakwenta kutsi babe eMiddle East kutsi bafuna kutsengisa emandla agezi, njengobe benta eEastern nase Southern Europe", washo ngekusho kwemininingwane.
Ngekusho kwaNdvunankhulu, kunetindlela netindlela tekulwa nalomsebenti waseRussia.
"IMelika inemandla, ngekusitwa ngumsebenti wemasotja aseMelika, kutsi icinisekise kutsi tindlela tekuhamba emantini tihlala tivulekile futsi, uma kudzingeka, tivalwe, kute kucinisekiswe kutsi emandla aseRussia angeke afakwe emakethe", kwasho yena.
ZinkÃ© abekhuluma emcimbini lobewuhanjelwe yi-Consumer Energy Alliance, lokuyinhlangano lengasebenti ngenzuzo lebitwa ngekutsi "livi lelabatsengi bemandla" eMelika.
Wacatsanisa indlela yase Washington yekubhekana neRussia ne Iran, watsi tifanana.
"Lendlela lengiyo yetezimali ku-Iran naseRussia, kutsi, kancane kancane, kusetjentiswe futsi kutsatselwe esikhundleni setintfo letiyinkimbinkimbi", kwasho yena, abhekisele eRussia njengentfo "leyenta tintfo letincane" ngobe inemnotfo loletsembele kutintfo letiyinkimbinkimbi.
Letimemetelo tentiwe ngesikhatsi hulumende wa Trump atsatsa umsebenti wekukhulisa kutfunyelwa kwegesi le-LNG yaseMelika eEurope, esikhundleni seRussia, lekungukona kubita kakhulu kubatsengi base Europe.
Kungako-ke, hulumende wa Trump, kufaka ekhatsi Mengameli Donald Trump, etama kucinisekisa iGermany kutsi iyekele umsebenti wayo 'longakafaneli' we Nord Stream 2 longasho kutsi i-Berlin itawuba "ngumkhumbi" wa Moscow.
I-Nord Stream 2, iphrojekthi lenemali letigidzigidzi leti-11 letotfutfukisa kukhokha kwemapayipi emanti, ibe ngemamitha latigidzi leti-110 emcumbi, imane nje iyindleko.
I-Kremlin itsi kuphikiswa lokukhulu kwe-Washington kulomsebenti kwentiwa ngetizatfu tetimali futsi kuyindlela yekungalingani.
"Ngicabanga kutsi siyavumelana ngekutsi emandla angeke abe yindlela yekucindzetela futsi batsengi kumele bakhone kukhetsa umphakeli wegesi labafuna kumnika yona", kusho iNdvuna yeMandla yaseRussia Alexander Novak ngemuva kwekuhlangana neNdvuna yeMandla yaseMelika Rick Perry eMoscow ngaSeptemba.
Lesimo seMelika sabangela kuphendvuka kweJalimane, leyagcizelela kutibophetela kwayo ekuchubekiseni lomsebenti.
Inhlangano yetimboni yaseJalimane, iBundesverband Deutscher Industrien (BDI), icele i-USA kutsi iyekele inchubomgomo ye-EU lemayelana nemandla agezi kanye netivumelwano te-Berlin neMoscow.
"Nginenkinga lenkhulu uma umuntfu wesitsatfu angenelela kutinsita tetfu temandla", kusho Dieter Kempf, umholi weBundesverband der Deutschen Industrien (BDI) ngemuva kwemhlangano wakhe nemengameli waseJalimane Angela Merkel kanye nemengameli waseRussia Vladimir Putin.
