I-Massachusetts Senator Elizabeth Warren, watsi ngeMgcibelo utawucabangisisa ngekukhetsa kwakhe kutsi abe ngumengameli ngemuva kwelukhetfo lolusemkhatsini.
Emhlanganweni welidolobha e-Hollywood, eMassachusetts, Warren wacinisekisa kutsi uyawucabangisisa ngalendzaba.
"Sikhatsi sesifikile sekutsi bafati baye eWashington futsi balungise hulumende wetfu lonenkinga, futsi loko kudzinga umfati lotawuba semkhatsini", kwasho yena, ngekusho kweThe Hill.
