Emave langu-18 kanye neSifundza saseColumbia asekela kuphikisana ngemtsetfo nemtsetfo lomusha waseMelika wekungavumeli bantfu labahlukunyetwa ngemacembu etenkholo nobe budlova basekhaya kutsi banikwe indzawo yekuhlala.
