Imizamo yekuphephisa bantfu ePalu njengobe linani lebantfu labafile liphindvwe kabili, nanobe kunemshikashika wekutfola labasindze
Bantfu labasindze kuleyo nhlekelele, bebachubeka baba timbi kakhulu.
"Kuvutsa kakhulu", kwasho make Risa Kusuma loneminyaka lengu-35 budzala, etama kusita umntfwana wakhe lonemkhuhlane endzaweni yekukhosela lebeyibekwe edolobheni lelidzabukile lasePalu.
"Tilondza letinsha tiletsa leminye imitimba njalo ngemzuzu.
Emanti lahlobile ayandza".
Labanye bantfu betama kubuyela emakhaya abo labeshonile, baphindze batfola tintfo tabo letisemantini, betama kusindzisa nobe yini lebebayitfola.
Emakhulu ebantfu alimala, futsi tibhedlela, letalimala ngenca yalokuzamazama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwafinyelela ku-7.5 ngekwe-Richter scale, takhona kuhlangabetana netidzingo.
Labanye labalimala, njenga Dewey Harris, lowaba netinhlungu emhlane nasegidzini, bahlala ngaphandle kweSibhedlela Semasotja ePalu, lapho khona lusito lwekucala beluniketwa ngaphandle ngenca yekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu.
Emehlo akhe agcwala tinyembeti ngesikhatsi akhuluma ngendlela lativa ngayo nakugadla kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu, lokwaphazamisa likamelo lakhe lelisesitezi sesihlanu ehhotela labelihlala kulo kanye nemkakhe nendvodzakati yakhe.
"Bekungekho sikhatsi sekusindziswa.
Ngatfola kutsi ngisebuhlungwini", Harris watjela i-Associated Press, wengeta watsi umndeni wakhe bewuselidolobheni kutewugubha umshado.
"Ngamuva umkami akhala acela lusito, kodvwa kwavele kwathula.
Angati kutsi kwentekani kuye nasengumntfwanami.
Ngiyetsemba kutsi baphephile".
LiBambela laseMelika licala iChina ngekwesaba "ngekutfumela tikhangiso"
Ngemuva kweliviki liphephandaba lelisemtsetfweni laseChina liphephephandzaba lelimakhasi lamane leliphephandzaba laseMelika lelikhuluma ngetintfo letitsite letitsintsa kutsengisa emkhatsini weMelika neChina, liBambela laseMelika eChina latsi iBeijing isebentisa emaphephandzaba aseMelika kute isakata inkhulumo yayo.
UMengameli waseMelika Donald Trump ukhulume ngaLwesitsatfu etincwadzini letibhaliselwe iChina Daily, letiphuma eDes Moines Register, liphephandaba lelisakatwa kakhulu e-Iowa, ngemuva kwekusola iChina ngekufuna kungenela lukhetfo lwe-Congress lwangaNovemba 6, lokuyintfo lephikwa yi-China.
Tinsolo taTrump tekutsi iBeijing yetama kungenela lukhetfo lwaseMelika, tichaze loko lokwachazwa yi-Reuters ngulabasebenti baseMelika kutsi ngulokusha kuloluhlelo lolunyenti lwe-Washington lwekucindzetela iChina.
Nanobe hulumende wangaphandle angavunyelwa kutsi akhangise ngekutsengisa, iBeijing neWashington nyalo sebayimphi yekutsengisa futsi sebacindzetele imphahla levela kulamanye emave.
Timali letiphindzisako taseChina ekucaleni kwemphi yekutsengisa betihlose kuhlasela batsengisi betimphahla letitsengisa emaveni lafana ne-Iowa lebeyisekela licembu le-Republican la-Trump, kusho bo-China kanye ne-US.
Terry Brandt, liNcusa laseMelika eChina kanye neliphatsi lelidze lase-Iowa, live lelisetulu lelikhokha kakhulu ekuhwebelaneni ngetekulima eChina, watsi iBeijing itsintse basebenti, balimi kanye nemabhizinisi aseMelika.
I-China, njengobe Brandt abhala encwadzini ye-Des Moines Register yangeLisontfo, "ivele yenta lokwesabisa ngekushicilela tikhangiso teluhlelo lwetentengiso ku-Free Press yetfu".
"Ngesikhatsi yetama kusakata lemfundziso, hulumende waseChina usebentisa emagugu aseMelika enkhululeko yekukhuluma kanye neyekushicilela, ngekushicilela sikhangiso lesikhokhelwako ku-Des Moines Register", kwabhala Brandstad.
"Ngalokuphambene, etitolo taseBeijing, utotfola emavi lambalwa laphikisako futsi kute lokumele kumelelwe imibono leyehlukene bantfu baseChina labanayo mayelana netinkinga tetemnotfo eChina, njengoba bemitfombo yetindzaba baniketwe ligunya le-CPC", wabhala.
Wengeta watsi "lenye yemaphephandzaba labaluleke kakhulu eChina ayizange ivume kushicilela" sihloko sakhe, nanobe angakatjeli kutsi ngubani.
EmaRiphabhulikhi ayekela kuvota labasikati ngenca yekwehluleka kwaCavanaugh, bahloli bayayicaphela lendzaba
Njengobe emaRiphabhulikhi lamanyenti lahloniphekile achubeka nekusekela Brett Kavanaugh lotawuba lijaji leNkantolo lePhakeme, nanobe sekunetinsolo tekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi, bahloli bayayicaphela indlela bantfu labangahle bavukele ngayo, ikakhulukati labasikati, kulolukhetfo lolusemkhatsini lolutako.
Imibono ngalendzaba ilukhuni futsi linyenti lemaRiphabhulikhi livete kutsi lifuna kuchubeka nekuvota.
Letintfo angeke tibe khona", kusho Grant Reyer, longuphrofesa wetemfundvo yepolitiki eSikolweni se-Maxwell eSyracuse University, nakakhuluma ngendzaba leyatfolakala ngaMgcibelo.
Reer ukhatsateka kutsi lesento semzuzu wekugcina seSenator Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) sekufuna luphenyo lwe-FBI sitawukwanela kuheha emavoti lanelulaka.
"Bafati angeke bakukhohlwe lokwentekile itolo, angeke bakukhohlwe kusasa, futsi angeke bakukhohlwe nakancane ngaNovemba", kusho Karin Jean-Pierre, umeluleki lomkhulu kanye nesikhulumi savelonkhe selicembu le-MoveOn, ngeLesihlanu, ngekusho kweliphephandzaba iWashington, D.C.
NgaLesihlanu ekuseni, bamemeteli behlabela ngekushesha batsi "November is coming!" egcumeni lelikhulu leSigungu Lesikhulu njengobe emaRiphabhulikhi labengamele Likomidi Letebulungiswa anika umlayeto lomusha wekuncuma Kavanaugh, ngisho nobe bekunofakazi longuDkt Christine Blazy Ford, kubika i-MIC.
"Inshisekelo kanye nesibindzi semaDemocrats kutawufika ezingeni lelisetulu", kusho Stu Rodenberg, longusihlaziyi lesatfola kuhlatiya, ku-website yetindzaba.
"Batsi seyivele iphezulu, futsi kuliciniso.
Kodvwa kungenteka kutsi lizinga lingaphasi, ikakhulukati kulabo labasikati labangafuni kuvota labasemadolobheni nasebantfwaneni labaseminyakeni lengu-18 kuya ku-29 budzala, labavame kungamemukeli umengameli nanobe bamtondza".
Ngisho nangaphambi kwekutsi Ford etfule bufakazi bakhe, lapho abeka khona imininingwane lemayelana nekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi kwaLoncumo lweNkantolo lePhakeme, bahloli bebabona kutsi kutawuba nemiphumela lemibi nangabe emaRiphabhulikhi achubeka nekugcotjwa.
"Lesi yintfo lematima kakhulu kuRiphabliki", kwasho Michael Steele, lobekangumengameli we-Republican National Committee, ekucaleni kweliviki leliphelile, ngekusho kwe-NBC News.
"Akusiyo nje incenye yekuhlola nobe incenye yekugcina yevoti nobe kutsi ngabe Kavanaugh utawuyekelwa yini, kepha yindlela emaRiphabhulikhi layisebentise ngayo lendzaba nekutsi aphatfwe njani", kusho Guy Cecil, longumcondzisi we-Priorities USA, licembu lelisita emaDemocrats ekuncumeni.
Nobe kunjalo, bantfu baseMelika babonakala bahlukene ekhatsi mayelana nekutsi ngubani lokufanele bamkholwe ngemuva kwekutfola bufakazi baFortune naCavanaugh, futsi batsandza kakhulu lona wesibili.
Luhlolo lolusha lwe-YouGov lukhombisa kutsi 41% webantfu labatiphendvulile bakukholelwa loko lokushiwo ngu-Ford, kantsi 35% batsi bakukholelwa loko lokushiwo ngu-Kavanaugh.
Ngetulu kwaloko, emaphesenti langu-38 atsi bacabanga kutsi Cavanaugh kungenteka nobe nakanjani ucabanga kutsi ucala emanga, kantsi emaphesenti langu-30 atsi naye Ford wacala emanga.
Ngemuva kwekushaya kwaFlake, i-FBI yatsatsa sinyatselo sekuphenya ngaFord kanye nalomunye umshushisi, Deborah Ramirez, kusho i-Guardian.
Ecinisweni, ecaleni lakhe, Ford wafakaza embikwemkhandlu weSigungu Lesengamele kutsi Kavanaugh wamhlasela ngesikhatsi adzakiwe ngesikhatsi aneminyaka lengu-17 budzala.
Ramirez utsi lomuntfu lofuna kuba lijaji leNkantolo lePhakeme wamkhombisa titfo takhe tekuyawubeleka ngesikhatsi basemcimbini ngesikhatsi bobabili bafundza e-Yale ngemnyaka wa 1980.
Umuntfu lowasungula iWebhu uhlela kucala i-Internet lensha kute ihlangabezane ne-Google ne-Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, longumsunguli we-Web, ucala inkapani lefuna kuchudzelana ne-Facebook, i-Amazon ne-Google.
Umuntfu lomusha lowenta lomsebenti wetekhompyutha ngu-Inrupt, lokusicumbi lesisekelwe ku-solids, lokusicumbi lesisemtsetfweni lesentiwa ngu-Berners Lee.
I-Solid iniketa basebentisi litfuba lekukhetsa kutsi idatha yabo igcinelwa kuphi nekutsi ngubani longafinyelela kulolwati.
Ku-Fast Company, Berners-Lee wahleka watsi injongo ye-Inrupt "yekuba ngumbusi wemhlaba wonkhe".
Watsi: "Kufanele sikwente nyalo".
"Lesi sikhatsi lesingumlandvo.
Loluhlelo lusebentisa buchwepheshe be-Solid platform kuvumela basebentisi kutsi bakhe 'indzawo yabo yekugcina idatha nge-elekthronikhi' nobe i-POD.
Ingase ibe netincwadzi telwati, tinhla temisebenti, umculu, incwadzi yemculo, naletinye tintfo takho kanye netemsebenti.
Kufana nekutsi iGoogle Drive, iMicrosoft Outlook, iSlack neSpotify tonkhe tiyatfolakala kusiphequluli sinye ngesikhatsi.
Sici lesiyingcayizivele sendzawo yekugcina idatha nge-elekthronikhi kutsi ivumela umsebentisi kutsi ancume kutsi ngubani longafinyelela kuloluhlobo lolutsite lwemininingwane.
Le-Company ikubita ngekutsi "kuciniswa ngemininingwane".
Umcondvo we-Inrupt, ngekusho kwe-CEO wayo, John Bruce, kutsi inkapani inikete imitfombolusito, tinchubo kanye nemakhono lafanele kute kutsi loluhlelo lwekwenta tintfo lufinyeleleke kubo bonkhe bantfu.
Le-Company yakhiwa ngu-Berners Lee, Bruce, umshini wekuphepha lowatsengwa yi-IBM, labanye bacambi labasebenta kulomsebenti kanye nemphakatsi webantfu labatisebentisako.
Kusukela kuleliviki, basebenti betinsita emhlabeni wonkhe bangakha tinhlelo tabo tekusebentisa emandla lavela ku-inrupt.
Berners-Lee watsi yena nelicembu lakhe abakakhulumi "ne-Facebook ne-Google mayelana nekutsi bayemukelwa yini kutsi bente tingucuko letinkhulu, bagucule emabhizinisi abo ngalanga linye.
"Asikatibuti kutsi bavumelekile yini".
Kulesinye sihloko lesishicilelwe ku-Medium ngaMgcibelo, Berners-Lee wabhala kutsi "umsebenti we-Inrupt kuniketa emandla etekuhweba kanye netinhlelo tekuphepha letitawuvikela bulunga kanye nelizinga le-web lensha leyakhiwe ngesisekelo se-Solid platform".
Nga-1994, Berners-Lee wagucula i-Internet ngesikhatsi asungula i-World Wide Web Consortium eMassachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT).
Etinyangeni letimbalwa letendlulile, Berners-Lee waba livi lelikhulu enkhulumeni yekungatingeni ku-Internet.
Ngisho nangesikhatsi sekusungulwa kwe-Inrupt, Berners Lee utawuhlala angumsunguli kanye nemcondzisi we-World Wide Web Consortium, i-Web Foundation kanye ne-Open Data Institute.
"Nginelitsemba lelikhulu nge-Internet letako", kwengeta Berners-Lee.
Bernard Van: Umfundisi Lowatfola Umchele WaseVictoria NgeMphi Yelive Yekucala
Umfundisi waseSheshi lowatfola umchele weVictoria ngesikhatsi asebentisa libutfo lemphi yeMphi yeMhlaba Yekucala, wahlonishwa ekhaya eminyakeni lelikhulu leyengcile.
Lisekela le-Colonel, uMfundisi Bernard Van watfola lomuda ngamhlaka 29 Inhlaba 1918, ngekuhlasela iBellenglise neLehaucourt.
Kodvwa-ke, wabulawa ngumuntfu lobekabulala bantfu labane ngemuva kwemalanga lamane futsi akazange atfole kutsi utfole umklomelo lomkhulu waseBrithani.
NgaMgcibelo, kwavulwa ligundvwe lelikhunjulwa batukulu bakhe lababili, lelalinyatwa ngemjaho eRasden, eNorthamptonshire.
Lomunye wetitukulwane takhe, Michael Van, watsi "kufanekisela kakhulu" kutsi lesigcilikati savalwa ngemnyaka welikhulu ngemuva kwesento sebudvodza semkhulu wakhe, lokwamenta watfola indondo.
Ngekusho kwe-London Gazette, ngaSeptember 29, 1918, Lt. Col. Van wahola libutfo lakhe eSan Kenedin Canal, etfuntini leliminyene futsi atsatfwa ngemaphini lanemandla".
Ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi, wagijima waya embili, futsi "ngesibindzi lesikhulu" wahola lomugca, ngaphambi kwekutsi ashaye ngemkhono wakhe, ashaya labatsatfu kulelicembu.
Lisekela leColonel Van labulawa ngumuntfu lobekabulala emaJalimane nga-October 4, 1918, cishe inyanga yinye ngaphambi kwekuphela kwemphi.
Michael Van, loneminyaka lengu-72, watsi tento tebuchawe ta-Gogo "bekuyintfo lengiyati kutsi angeke ngiyifinyelele, intfo leyenta umuntfu ative ahlonipheke kakhulu".
Yena nemnakabo, Dokotela James Van, baphindze bafaka indandatho ngemuva kwalomkhosi, lobewuholwa yi Brentwood Imperial Youth Band.
Michael Van watsi "wajabula kakhulu kuba kulelo parade" futsi wengeta watsi "sibindzi selihhashi sibonakala ngekusekelwa bantfu labanyenti".
