Mikkelsen longekho esimeni lesifanele utawugcwala esihlalweni ngeMgcibelo eRyder Cup
Phil Mickelson waseMelika utawushaya lirekhodi lelikhulu ngeLisontfo, nakadlala umdlalo wakhe wemnyaka wema-47 we-Ryder Cup, kodvwa kufanele ente lokunyenti kute angabukwa ngetizatfu letingakalungi.
Mickelson, lowenta umnyaka wekucala (lokungumnyaka lodze) wekubamba umncintiswano lobalelwa eminyakeni lemibili, waphocelelwa ngumholi Jim Furyk kutsi ahlale ebhentshini emidlalweni ye-fourball ne-foursome ngaLesibili.
Esikhundleni sekutsi abe nguloyo loholako njengobe kuvamile eMelika, lomdlali lophumelele emahlandla lasihlanu wacitse lilanga lonkhe atfola emandla futsi asebenta, etsemba kutsi utawulungisa tinkinga takhe.
Ngaphandle kwekutsi kube nemshayeli locondze kakhulu ngisho nasesikhatsini sekuphakama kwakhe, lomdlalo walomuntfu loneminyaka lengu-48 budzala awukabaluleki kuleyo ndzawo lencane yeLe Golf National, lapho khona emabanga lamadze avame kuba matima.
Njengobe lomdlalo bewungekho ngaphansi, Mikkelsen, emdlalweni wakhe wesitsatfu ngeLisontfo, ubhekene naFrancesco Molinari, umpetha we-British Open, lobekahlele kanye naTommy Fleetwood, lowetayele kuba ngumdlali lomusha, kute bancobe yonkhe imidlalo yabo lemine kuleliviki.
