Kusasa kutawuba ngulenye inhlobo yesilwane.
Kusasa kutawubaluleka kutsi umuntfu ente njani, futsi loko kuhlukile.
Kumnandzi kuba semkhatsini webadlali uma tintfo tihamba kahle, kodvwa nawusemkhatsini webadlali labakhulu nawusemkhatsini webadlali labakhulu, usuke utikhandza usemkhatsini webadlali labakhulu.
Lona ngumlayeto lokufanele uwudlulisele kubadlali, kutsi bangakhona njani kusasa.
