"Ngikhumbula onkhe emagama akhe", waphendvula nakabutwa kutsi Ben Crenshaw, lobekangumphatsi nga-1999, wababutsa njani badlali bakhe ngelilanga lekugcina.
"Sinemidlalo lemikhulu lengu-12 kusasa, kodvwa sifuna kucala masinyane njengaseBrookline, njengaseMedinah.
Nasitfola lomfutfo, kuba nekucindzeteleka lokukhulu kulemidlalo lesemkhatsini.
Senta sincumo saloko lesikufunako, futsi sisuke setama kwenta lomlingo ngakusasa".
