"Ngikhetse lelicembu ngaloluhlelo ngobe ngicabanga kutsi lihlanganisa yonkhe indlela", kusho Bjorn, acondzisa kukhetsa kwakhe kuma singles.
Kuyekela kabusha kwemkhumbi lomusha wemphi waseJalimane
Lelihhashi lelisha lemphi laseJalimane bekufanele lifike ngemnyaka wa 2014, kute libuyisele imikhumbi yemphi leseyigugile ngesikhatsi seMphi yeBudlova, kepha angeke lifike ngemnyaka lotako, ngenca yetintfo letite emaphutsa kanye netindleko letinyukile, kubikwa ngemitfombo yetindzaba.
Kusebenta kweRheinland-Pfalz, umkhumbi lomkhulu we Baden-Wuerttemberg class, sekubekelwe sikhatsi sekugcina, kuya enyangeni yekucala ya 2019, kusho liphephandaba iDie Zeit, lelicaphuna sikhulumi semabutfo.
Lomkhumbi bekufanele ngabe wajoyina Luphiko Lwemabutfo AseMelika nga-2014, kepha tinkinga tekutfola tintfo letitsite betibalulekile kuloluhlelo lolunemandla.
Letikebhe letine teBaden-Wuerttemberg letibekwe licala liTiko leTemphi nga-2007 titawufaka esikhundleni semabutfo lamadzala lase Bremen.
Titawugcwala umshayakhadi lonemandla, tinhlobo letehlukene temachinga lahlaselako kanye nemikhumbi, kanye naletinye tindlela tekusebentisa umshini wekubonisa, njengekunciphisa i-radar, i-infrared kanye nekubhala.
Lokunye lokubalulekile kutsi kuncishiswa kwelizinga lemisebenti yekunakekela njengobe letintfo letinsha tingasetjentiswa iminyaka lemibili ngaphandle kwemaphothi aseJalimane.
Nobe kunjalo, lokubambezeleka lokungapheli kusho kutsi nanobe lemikhumbi yetemphi ibitwa ngekutsi ingumshini wekugcina, itawuvumela iGerman kutsi ikhombise emandla ayo kulamanye emave, kuze kube ngulapho seyivele isetjentisiwe, kusho iDie Zeit.
Le F125 lebeyingajabulisi yavela etinhlokweni temilandvo emnyakeni lowengcile, ngesikhatsi le German Navy ivuma kutsi ayiyitsatsi lenkhumbi, yabuye yayibuyisela emuva eBlohm & Voss shipyard lese Hamburg.
Bekukwekucala ngca kutsi Lusotja lwemphi lubuyisele umkhumbi endzaweni yekwakha ngemuva kwekutfunjwa.
Kute lwati lolunyenti lolwatfolakala mayelana netizatfu tekubuyiswa, kepha ema-German akhuluma ngetintfo letinyenti "letingahambelani netinhlelo kanye netintfo letisetjentiswako" letitawenta kutsi umkhumbi wemphi ungabi nemsebenti uma ngabe usetjentiswe emphini.
Tinkinga telusito lwesoftware betibaluleke kakhulu. ngobe imikhumbi yelicembu le Baden-Wuerttemberg inemalunga emkhumbi lalikhulu nemashumi lamabili, ihhafu nje kuphela kunalemikhumbi yelicembu le Bremen.
Kwaphindze kwembulwa kutsi lenkhumbi inesisindvo lesisetulu kakhulu, lokunciphisa kusebenta kwayo futsi kuvimbela likhono lemkhumbi wetimbuti kutsi ungete wavuselelwa esikhatsini lesitako.
Le Rhineland-Pfalz lengemathani langu 7000, itsatfwa ngekutsi inesisindvo lesiphindvwe kabili kunesemikhumbi yesigaba lesifanako leyasetjentiswa ngemaJalimane ngeMphi yeLive Yesibili.
Ngaphandle kwemishini lephukile, tindleko talomsebenti (lokufaka ekhatsi kuceceshwa kwebasebenti) nako kwaba yinkinga.
Kutsiwa seyifinyelele ku-EUR 3,1 billion (EUR 3,6 billion), kantsi bekune-EUR 2,2 billion ekucaleni.
Tinkinga letitsintsa emafrigate lamasha tibaluleke kakhulu njengoba emandla emkhumbi waseGermany ahamba kancane.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, Hans-Peter Bartels, lowengamele likomidi lelivumela kusebenta kwetintfo letitsite, wavuma kutsi emabutfo emphi "asetawuphela masinyane".
Lesikhulu satsi inkinga yakhula ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi, ngobe imikhumbi lendzala yacitfwa, kodvwa kute leminye leyayingayitsatsa.
Watsi kute ngisho namunye emabhasikidi aseBaden-Wuerttemberg lakhona kutsi angenele umbutfo wemasotja aseMphini.
I-National Trust isilalele imfihlo yemabhathayithi
Lucwaningo lolusha lolwentiwa ensimini yaseScotland, lufuna kuveta kutsi emalulwane ayisebentisa njani lendzawo nakadla.
Lokutfolwa kutawuchaza indlela letilwane letihamba ngayo futsi kutawusita ekuhleleni tinyatselo letitawutsatfwa esikhatsini lesitako kute kuvikelwe imvelo.
Lolucwaningo lolwentiwa bososayensi baseScotland, i-National Trust, lutawuhlola indlela leyenta ngayo iminenkhe lencane kanye neminenkhe lencane, kanye neminenkhe lemnyama kanye neminenkhe yaseDubbendo e-Inverewe Gardens, eWester Ross.
Ema-logger lamasha atawufakwa etindzaweni letibalulekile letisedvute nalelibala lelikhulako kute kubonwe imisebenti yemabhatkhati kulo lonkhe lelichinga.
Basebenti be-NTS kanye nemavolontiya batawenta futsi lucwaningo loluhambako basebentisa tinzwa letisetjentiswa ngesandla.
Kuhlolwa kwemisindvo yawo onkhe emarekhodi kutawuveta kutsi mangakhi emabhatti laphindze akhulume, nekutsi nguwaphi emacembu lanjalo.
Ngemuva kwaloko, kutawukhicitwa imephu yendzawo kanye nembiko kute kubonakale kahle kutsi tilwane tiphila njani.
Rob Dewar, umeluleki wekuphepha kwemvelo ku-NTS, uncoma kutsi imiphumela itawukhombisa kutsi nguyiphi indzawo lebalulekile kubologwaja nekutsi isetjentiswa njani nguleyo naleyo nhlobo.
Lolwati lutosita ekutsini kubonakale tinzuzo tekuphatsa tindzawo tekuhlala, njengekwakha emadlelo kanye nendlela lencono yekugcina emahlatsi emalulwane kanye naletinye tilwane letihlobene nawo.
Emasotja aseScotland kanye ne-United Kingdom, anciphe kakhulu kusukela ngelikhulu leminyaka lelidlulile.
Tiyasongelwa ngumsebenti wekwakha kanye nekutfutfukiswa kwetindzawo letihlala tona, lokuyintfo leyenta kutsi tindzawo tekuhlala tibe tindzala futsi tibulale indzawo yato.
Imishini yemoya kanye nekukhanya nako kuyingoti, kanye netincwadzi letitsintsa timbalesi kanye nemakhemikhali lasebentiswa ekwakheni, kanye nekuhlaselwa ngemakati.
Emalulwane akaboni.
Njengobe tilwane letiphila emhlabatsini tifuna kudla ebusuku, tindlebe tato tiyasebenta kakhulu kunemehlo ato.
Tisebentisa indlela lematima yekubhala kute titfole tilwanyana kanye netintfo letingaba yingoti endleleni yato.
I-NTS, lecaphela tindlu temlandvo letingetulu kwa-270, tivande letisemagcekeni langu-38 kanye nemahekitha langu-76 000 emhlaba eveni lonkhe, ibuka timphungane njengaletisisekelo.
Inetati letilishumi leticeceshiwe letihlale tihlola, tihlole tindzawo lapho kubhace khona emalulwane futsi ngalesinye sikhatsi tiwancobe.
I-WUA iphindze yakha indzawo yekucala yaseScotland yekukhosela emalulwane endzaweni yaseTheave, eDumphris naseGalway, lapho kuhlala khona tilwane letisiphohlongo kuletingu-10 taseScotland.
Umphatsi walendzawo, David Thompson, utsi lendzawo iyindzawo lekahle yekubamba emalulwane.
Watsi: "Lapha eTheave sinendzawo lenhle kakhulu yekubhukusha".
"Sinetakhiwo takadzeni, tihlahla letinkhulu netindzawo letinhle tekuhlala.
Kusekunyenti lesingakwati ngalemibungu, ngako umsebenti lesiwenta lapha nalamanye emave utawusisita kutsi sikucondze kahle loko lokudzingekako kute tibe nemihlambi leminyenti".
Uphindze agcizelele kutsi kubalulekile kuhlolwa kwato tonkhe tilwane ngaphambi kwekutsi kwentiwe umsebenti wekunakekela tindlu, ngobe kubulala lidladla linye kungabulala tilwane letinsikati letingu-400 kanye naletincane, futsi kungabulala bonkhe bantfu labakhona.
Emalulwane ayintfo levikelwe futsi akuvunyelwa kutsi abulawe, ahlukunyetwe, noma aphatamiseke, noma abhidlitwe.
Elizabeth Ferrell, losebenta eScotland, lobekacondziswe kuBat Conservation Trust, wakhutsata bantfu kutsi basite.
Watsi: "Kuningi lokusamele sikufundze ngemabhatkhati etfu, futsi kanyenti, kute lesikwati ngemabhatkhati etfu".
Ronaldo uphika emacala ekudlwengula njengobe bameli bakhe balungiselela kumangalela magazini waseJalimane
Cristiano Ronaldo wabita letinsolo tekudlwengulwa kwakhe ngekutsi "tingemanga", watsi labanye "bafuna kutiphakamisa" basebentisa ligama lakhe.
Bameli bakhe batawumangalela i-Der Spiegel, liphephandzaba laseJalimane lelakhipha letinsolo.
Lomdlali we-Portugal kanye ne-Juventus usolwa ngekudlwengula umfati waseMelika lokutsiwa ngu-Catherine Mayorgga, ekamelweni lakhe lasehhotela eLas Vegas nga-2009.
Ngekusho kwalelicala, bekutsiwa wamkhokhela imali lengu-R375,000 kutsi angamtsintsi kutsi akhulume ngalendzaba, kusho i-Der Spiegel ngaLesihlanu.
Akhuluma ngeli-video live ku-Instagram kubalandeli bakhe labatigidzi letingu-142 ngemuva kwekumangalelwa, Ronaldo, loneminyaka lengu-33 budzala, wabita letindzaba ngekutsi "tindzaba temanga".
"Cha, cha, cha, cha, cha.
Loko lokushiwo lamuhla kungumlayeto longemanga", kwasho lomdlali lophumelele emahlandla lasihlanu i-Golden Ball ku-TV.
"Bafuna kutiphakamisa futsi basebentisa libito lami.
Kuvamile.
Bafuna kudvunyiswa ngelibito lami, kodvwa loku kuyincenye yemsebenti wami.
Ngiyajabula futsi konkhe kulungile", kwasho lomdlali amomotseka.
Bameli baRonaldo balungiselela kumangalela i-Der Spiegel ngetindzaba letishicilelwe, labatsi "kubika lokungemukeleki kwetindzaba letitsintsa imphilo yemuntfu", ngekusho kwe-Reuters.
Ummeli Christian Skerch watsi lomdlali utawufuna umonakalo "ngekuhlukunyetwa ngekutiphatsa lokulingana nebubi baloluhlobo, lokungenteka kutsi ngulenye yetintfo letimbi kakhulu letenteke kumuntfu ngekumfihlo eminyakeni lembalwa leyengcile".
Lesento lesitsite sitsi senzeka ngaJuni 2009 ehhotela laseLas Vegas.
Ngemuva kwekuhlangana e-nightclub, Ronaldo naMayorga babuyela ekamelweni lalomdlali, lapho abetfuke khona, ngekusho kwemiculu leyafakwa eNkantolo yeSifundza yaseClark County, eNevada.
Mayorca utsi Ronaldo waguca ngemadvolo ngemuva kwaloku lokutsiwa kwenteke futsi wamtjela kutsi "99%" bekayindvodza "lehle" kodvwa waphatfwa kabi ngu "linye%".
Lemiculu iveta kutsi Ronaldo uyavuma kutsi bebaphindze balalane, kodvwa loko bekungemvumo yabo.
Mayorgha uphindze atsi waya emaphoyiseni nasesibhedlela lapho atsatsa khona titfombe tetilondza takhe, kodvwa ngemuva kwaloko wavuma kutsi batemhlalisa ngaphandle kwenkantolo ngobe "abesaba kutsi utawuphindziselwa" futsi akhatsateke ngekutsi utawudliwa "ngumuntfu".
Lomake loneminyaka lengu-34 utsi wetama kuwucedza lomshado njengobe achubeka anenkinga ye-PTSD ngenca yaloko lokutsiwa kwentekile.
Ronaldo abeseceleni kwekutfunyelwa e-Real Madrid asuka eManchester United ngesikhatsi sekuhlukunyetwa, futsi kulenyanga yeLihlobo watfutsela e-Juventus yase-Italy, watfola imali lengemarandi latigidzi letilikhulu.
Brexit: UK 'itawutilela' kulahlekelwa ngumkhicito wetimoto
INdvuna yeTemabhizinisi, Greg Clark, itsi i-UK "itawutilahla ingunaphakadze" uma ingalahlekelwa ludvumo lwayo njenge-leader yemhlaba kutemoto ngemuva kwe-Brexit.
Wengeta watsi "kuyakhatsatisa" kutsi iToyota UK yatsi ku-BBC kutsi uma i-UK ishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano, itawuyekela kukhicita esiteshini sayo eBernaston, edvute naseDerby.
"Sidzinga sivumelwano", kwasho Mnu. Clark.
I-Japanese automaker yatsi umtselela wekubambezeleka kwe-cross-border uma ngabe i-Brexit ingekho sivumelwano, kungabhidlita imisebenti.
Lelihhovisi laseBernaston, lapho kwakhiwa khona i-Auris ne-Avensis, yakha timoto letingu-150.000 ngemnyaka lophelile, letingu-90 ekhulwini tato tatfunyelwa kulamanye emave e-European Union.
"Imibono yami kutsi uma iBrithani ishiya i-EU ekupheleni kwenyanga yeNdlovulenkhulu, kutawuyekwa kukhicita esiteshini setfu", kwasho Marvin Cook, umphatsi we-Toyota eBernaston.
Labanye bakhiciti betimoto base-UK nabo bakhulume ngetinsayeya tekuphuma e-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano mayelana nekutsengisa emaveni ngemave, kufana neHonda, iBMW kanye neJaguar Land Rover.
Sibonelo, iBMW, itsi itawuvala sikhungo sayo seMini eOxford inyanga yinye ngemuva kwe-Brexit.
Tinkinga letinkhulu tifaka ekhatsi tingoti letingaba khona kuloluhlelo lwekutsengisa timoto uma ngabe i-Brexit ingekho sivumelwano.
Umshini wekukhicita weToyota ulandzela indlela ye-just-in-time. Tincenye tifika njalo ngemaminitsi langu-37 kusuka kubatsengisi base-UK kanye nase-EU kwentela timoto letakhiwe ngetinjongo tekutsengiswa.
Uma ngabe i-UK ishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano mhlaka-29 kuMashi, kutawuba netinkinga eminyeleni, lokungaholela ekubambeni sikhatsi kanye nekushoda kwetintfo tekusebenta ngekulandzela umkhakha.
Bekungeke kwenteke kutsi iToyota igcine tintfo tekwakha ngetulu kwelilanga linye kulelihhovisi layo eDerbyshire, kusho le nkampani, ngako-ke umkhicito bewutawuyekela.
UMnu Clarke watsi luhlelo lwa-Theresa May lwebudlelwane belikusasa ne-EU "lufuna kucedza inkinga yekuhlola emave ngemave".
"Sidzinga sivumelwano. Sifuna sivumelwano lesincono kakhulu lesingasenta singatfoli nje kuphela imphumelelo yesikhashana, kodvwa sisebentise lelitfuba", washo ku-BBC Radio 4's Today programme.
"Leti tibonakaliso letisuka kuToyota kanye nakuletinye takhi tetintfo letitititfolakalako kutsi kumele kucinisekiswe kuchubeka kwemikhicito".
I-Toyota beyingakwati kukhuluma ngekutsi itawuyekela kukhicita malini, kepha yacaphela kutsi esikhatsini lesidze, letindleko letengetiwe titawunciphisa kukhicita kwefektri futsi ekugcineni tibulale imisebenti.
Peter Tshuvallari, losebente eBernaston iminyaka lengu-24 futsi lowengamele umbutfo we-Unite kulelihhovisi, watsi emalunga alelibhodi ayesaba kakhulu: "Ngekubona kwami, nangabe lemisebenti ilahleka, angeke iphindze ibuye.
Sikhulumi sahulumende satsi: 'Sivete luhlelo lolucondzile nalolunemandla lolumayelana nebudlelwane betfu ne-EU esikhatsini lesitako.'
Umhlangano waTrump naRosenstein ungahle ucitseke futsi, kusho iWhite House
Umhlangano lobalulekile waDonald Trump neLisekela leMshushisi Jikelele Rod Rosenstein "ungehlelwa ngulomunye liviki" njengobe kuchubeka imphi ngeSikhulu Lesikhulu Lesengamele, Brett Kavanaugh, kusho iWhite House ngeLisontfo.
Rosenstein wengamela umsebenti wemphenyi loyingcwelengcwele Robert Mueller, lophenya ngekungenelela kweRussia elukhetfweni, kuchumana kwebasebenti baTrump neRussia kanye nekungenelela kwemtsetfo lokungaba khona.
Lokutsi Trump angacosha liSekela leMengameli, lokubeka bungeneleli baMueller engotini, sekuyintfo lebekukhulunywa ngayo eWashington tinyanga letinyenti.
Ekucaleni kwalenyanga, i-New York Times yabika kutsi Rosenstein ucoce ngekugcoka umshina wekubamba tinhlayiya kute kukhonjiswe kukhulumisana kwakhe na Trump, lokwenta kutsi kube nekuhlukunyetwa kwemengameli ngekulandzela luCwebu lwema-25.
Rosenstein wawala kutsi abike.
Nanobe kunjalo, ngeMsombuluko lowengcile waya eNdlini leMhlophe, ngesikhatsi kunetindzaba tekutsi utawutsatsa sikhundla.
Esikhundleni saloko, bekutawubanjwa umhlangano ngaLesine naTrump, lobekahlala e-UN eNew York.
Trump watsi "ubengatsandza" kungamshiyi Rosenstein, kodvwa lomhlangano wahlehliswa kuze ungafiki ngesikhatsi sekulalelwa kwelicala leKhomishane yeTemtsetfo lapho khona Kavanaugh kanye nalomunye walabesifazane labamsola ngekumhlukubeta, Dokotela Christine Blazy Ford, bafakaza.
NgaLesihlanu, Trump wayala i-FBI kutsi yente luphenyo ngekhatsi kweliviki mayelana netinsolo letimayelana naKavanaugh, lokwabuye kwacedza sikhatsi sekubekwa kwe-Senate.
Sarah Sanders, losikhulumi saTrump, wavela ku-Fox News Sunday.
Nakabutwa mayelana nemhlangano wakhe naRosenstein, watsi: "Sikhatsi asikasekelwa, kungenteka kutsi kwenteke kuleliviki, kepha kungenteka kutsi kwenteke kulelinye liviki ngenca yato tonkhe letinye tindzaba letisemtsetfweni letibhekene neNkantolo lePhakeme.
Kodvwa sitawufundza ngako, futsi ngitsandza kutjela bomabomu".
Labanye batfu bemitfombo yetindzaba baphikisana nalombiko: Sanders akazange abambe inkhulumo yetindzaba eWhithouse kusukela ngaSeptemba 10.
Umhlahlandlela Chris Wallace wabuta kutsi kungani loku kwenteka.
Sanders waphendvula ngekutsi lokuncipha kwekwatiswa bekungasiko kwekwenyanya 'kubukeka' kwebantfu labatsintsekako ku-TV, nanobe atsi: "Ngingeke ngiphikisane nekutsi bayabonakala".
Ngemuva kwaloko, waveta kutsi kutawukhula kuchumana lokucondzile emkhatsini waTrump kanye nebatfumli.
"Mengameli uniketa tinhlolokhono letinyenti kwendlula nobe ngumuphi lomunye umengameli", washo, wengeta ngaphandle kwekusho kutsi: "Sibukene naletinombolo".
Kutawubanjwa imibuto, kusho Sanders, kodvwa "uma lomuntfu abengabuta umbuto kumengameli waseMelika, loko kungaba ncono kakhulu kunekukhuluma nami.
Sesetame kukwenta loku kanyenti, futsi niyakubona kutsi sesikwenta kanyenti emavikini lambalwa lendlulile, futsi kutawutsi esikhundleni saloko nitfole litfuba lekukhuluma nemengameli waseMelika".
Trump uvame kubuta imibuto uma ashiya iWhite House nobe ahlanganyela etinhlanganweni temphakatsi nobe etincociswaneni netindvuna.
Tincociswano temaphephandzaba letitsite ativami.
Kuloviki eNew York, umengameli waveta kutsi kungani loku kwenteka, ngekwenta intfo lengakavami futsi ngalesinye sikhatsi leyehlukile kubantfu labamemetela tindzaba.
INdvuna Yetemphilo ikhipha incwadzi kubantfu base-EU labasebenta eScotland National Health System, ngenca yekwesaba i-Brexit
INdvuna yeTemphilo yatfumela incwadzi kubantfu base-EU labasebenta eScotland's National Health Service, ikhombisa kubonga kwayo futsi ifisa kutsi bahlale ngemuva kwekuvalelwa kwe-UK e-European Union.
Jean Freeman, lilunga le-Scotland, watfumela incwadzi ngesikhatsi kusele tinyanga letisitfupha kutsi i-UK iphume e-EU.
Hulumende waseScotland sewuvele utibophelele kutsi utawufaka tindleko tekufaka sicelo sesimo sekuhlala sikhatsi lesidze (settled status) kubantfu base-EU labasebenta kuhulumende wakhe lophatselene netindzaba temphakatsi.
Nks Freeman wabhala encwadzini yakhe: 'Tinkhulumiswano emkhatsini we-UK ne-EU ngekuphuma tiqhubeke ngesikhatsi sasehlobo futsi ticondze ekutsini kutawutsatfwa tincumo ngekwindla.
Nanobe kunjalo, hulumende wase-UK naye sewuphindze walungiselela simo lesingahle sivele sekute sivumelwano.
Ngiyati kutsi lesi sikhatsi lesimatima kini nonkhe.
Kungako-ke ngifuna kuphindze ngivete kutsi ngiyayitsandza kakhulu iminikelo levela kubo bonkhe basebenti, kungakhatsaleki kutsi bavephi.
Tisebenti letisuka kulo lonkhe lelive le-EU kanye nalamanye emave tiletsa lwati lolubalulekile kanye nemakhono latawuphucula umsebenti wetemphilo, futsi kuzuze tigulane kanye nemimango lesiyisebentelako.
Scotland likhaya lakho futsi sifuna uhlale khona".
Christian Abercrombie uyahlindvwa ngemuva kwekulimala enhloko.
Umdlali weTennessee State Tigers, Christian Abercroby, ucitfwe masinyane ngemuva kwekuhlukunyetwa inhloko ngemuva kwekuhlukunyetwa inhloko emdlalweni waMgcibelo, lapho emaTiger ehlelwe ngemaphuzu langu-31 kuya ku-27 ngemaVanderbilt Commodores, kusho Mike Organ, longumhleli weTennessean.
Umchubi lomkhulu weTennessee State, Rod Reed, watjela batfumeli betindzaba kutsi lokulimala kwenteke ngaphambi nje kwekutsi kube nesikhatsi sekuphela kwemdlalo.
"Wafika wacondza kulelo bhande, wavele wavele wavele wavele walala", kwasho Reid.
Baceceshi kanye nemasotja banika Abercrombie umoya lophefumulako, bamfaka emgodleni, base bayamtsatsa bayomhlolisisa.
Lenye inceku leseTennessee State yatsi kuChris Harris ku-WSMV leseNashville, Tennessee, kutsi Ambercrombie sewukhululiwe e-Vanderbilt Medical Center.
Harris wengeta ngekutsi kute "lwati lolusolo lukhona mayelana neluhlobo/lusayizi walokulimala" futsi iTennessee State itama kutfola kutsi lokulimala kwenteka nini.
Umfundzi loyedvwa lofundza ngemnyaka wesibili (lowatiwa ngekutsi yi "redshirt") Abecroby, usemnyakeni wakhe wekucala e-Tennessee State ngemuva kwekutfutsa e-Illinois.
Wenta ema-takes lasihlanu ngeMgcibelo ngaphambi kwekutsi ashiye lomdlalo, lokwenta kutsi kube ngu-18 ngemnyaka.
Batsengi bangaphandle batawukhokhiswa imali lephakeme yekubhalisa uma batsenga imphahla e-UK
Labatsengi bangaphandle batawukhokhiswa imali lephakeme yekutsengisa timphahla tekutsenga emakhaya e-UK, kantsi imali lengetiwe itawusetjentiswa kuniketa lusito kubantfu labangenamakhaya, ngekusho kwemiklamo lemisha ya-Toris,
Lesento sitawubangela kutsi kube matima ngemkhankhaso waCorbyn wekudvonsela bantfu labasha kutsi bavote.
Kukhuphuka kwemali yekubhadala kutokhokhelwa batsengi labangakhokhi umtselo e-UK
LiTiko leTemnotfo lifuna kukhokha tigidzi temali letingu-R120 ngemnyaka - kute kusitwe bantfu labangenabo umsebenti
Batsengi bangaphandle batawucala kukhokhiswa imali lephakeme yekutsengisa timphahla tabo e-UK, kantsi imali lengetiwe itawusetjentiswa kusita bantfu labangenabo indzawo, njengobe Theresa May atawumemetela lamuhla.
Lesento sitawuchazwa njengentfo leyenta kube melula kutsi Jeremy Corbyn akwati kuvota bantfu labasha ngekutjela bantfu kutsi utawubapha tindlu letidulile futsi akwati nekubhekisa kubantfu labahola kakhulu.
Lenyuswe imali yekubhadala itawukhokhelwa bantfu labangakakhokhiswa umtselo e-UK, kantsi imali lengetiwe itawuphindze isite hulumende ekulweni nekweswelakala kwetindlu.
Lenyuselo lebhadalwa etinhlawulweni letikhona te-credit card, kanye nemazinga lasetulu etetimali lacala eminyakeni lemibili leyengcile ekutsengweni kwendlu yesibili kanye netindlu tekucashisa, ingafinyelela kumaphesenti lamatsatfu.
LiTiko leTemnotfo licabanga kutsi lesinyatselo sitawuletsa emali lengemarandi langu-120 ngemnyaka.
Kulinganiselwa kutsi emaphesenti langu-13 emakhaya lamasha eLondon atsengwa bantfu labangakahlali e-UK, lokwenta kutsi kubete tindleko futsi kwenta kube matima kakhulu kubantfu labasacala kutsenga emakhaya kutsi bangene emakethe yetindlu.
Tindzawo letinyenti leticebile kulelive - ikakhulukati enhlokodolobha - setigucuke taba "tidolobha letiliphutsa" ngenca yelinani lelikhulu lebatsengi labangaphandle labachitse sikhatsi sabo lesinyenti ngaphandle kwelive.
Lomgomo lomusha ufaka ekhatsi emaviki lambalwa ngemuva kwekutsi Boris Johnson acele kwehliswa kwemali yekubhalisa, kute bantfu labasha labanyenti batfole indzawo yabo yekucala yekuhlala.
Wasola tinkampani letinkhulu tekwakha ngekugcina tindlu tibi kakhulu, ngekutsatsa umhlaba ngaphandle kwekusebentisa wona, futsi wacela Make May kutsi asuse tici tetindlu letitsite kute abuyisele "lihlazo lekuhlala" eBritain.
Corbyn wamemetela luhlelo loluhle lwekugucula tindlu, loluhlanganisa kuhlolwa kwetindlu kanye nekucedza kucosha bantfu "ngaphandle kwesizatfu".
Uphindze afune kuniketa emalunga elikomidi lelikhulu emandla ekwakha tindlu letinsha.
May watsi: "Ngemnyaka lophelile ngatsi ngitawutinikela njengeNdvunankhulu ekuvuseleleni liphupho laseBrithani - kwenta imphilo ibe ncono etitukulwaneni letinsha.
Loku kusho kutsi kufanele silungise imakethe yetindlu lebhidlikile.
I-Britain itawuvulekela bantfu labafuna kuhlala, basebente futsi bakhe imphilo yabo lapha.
Nanobe kunjalo, bekungeke kulunge kutsi bantfu labangakahlali e-UK kanye netinkampani letiseveni langaphandle batsenge tindlu kalula njengebantfu baseBrithani labasebenta kamatima.
Bantfu labanyenti baphelelwa litsemba lekuba nemakhaya abo, futsi kuba bete tindlu akusasiyo intfo lembi".
Jack Ross: "Injongo yami lenkhulu kucecesha licembu laseScotland".
Umholi weSunderland, Jack Ross, utsi "kufisa kwakhe lokukhulu" kutsi ngalelinye lilanga abe ngumphatsi welicembu lesive laseScotland.
Lomdlali waseScotland loneminyaka lengu-42 budzala, ujabulile ngekuhlangabetana nalolucingo lwekuhlangabetana nelicembu laseNgilandi lese nyakatfo-mpumalanga, lelisesigabeni sesitsatfu ku-League One, emamaki lamatsatfu ngephansi kwelasezingeni lelisetulu.
Waya eSitediyamu seLitje ehlobo, ngemuva kwekubamba iSt Mirren wayivusa eScotland League kuleliviki leliphelile.
"Bengifuna kumelela live lami njengemdlali.
Ngatfola sicelo selicembu lesibili lesive, futsi kwaba njalo", kusho Ross ku-BBC Scotland ku-Sportsound.
"Kodvwa ngakhula ngibuka licembu laseScotland eHambden njalo nami babe ngisengumntfwana, futsi loko bekungigcina ngicabanga ngako.
Kodvwa lelitfuba litawufika kuphela nangabe ngikhone kucecesha emacembu".
Labangembili kwaRoss eSunderland nguDick Advocat, David Moyes, Sam Allardyce, Martin O'Neill, Roy Keane, Gus Poyet kanye naPaolo Di Canio.
Lomceceshi wangaphambilini we-Aloe Athletic utsi akazange esabe ngesikhatsi atjelwa kutsi alandzele emagama lasesikhundleni lesisetulu kulelive lelikhulu, ngobe bekakadze alele tindlela tekufuna ema-Barnsley ne-Ipswich Town.
"Njengamanje, imphumelelo yami itakwehlukaniswa yimpendvulo yembuzo lotsi: 'Ngingayibuyisela yini lelicembu ku-Premier League?'
Ngenca yesakhiwo salendzawo, lelicembu lingena e-Premier League", kwasho yena.
"Akukapheli lutfo kufika lapho, kodvwa kungenteka ngiticabange ngimphumelele lapha kuphela nangabe ngingakhona kubuyisela lelicembu".
Ross wacala umsebenti wakhe wekucecesha eminyakeni lemitsatfu leyengcile, ngemuva kwekucitsa sikhatsi lesitsite angumsiti wemceceshi eDubarton kanye netinyanga letingu-15 eHarts.
Wase usita iAloe kutsi iphindze ibuyele emuva kusuka ekulahlekelweni kuya esigabeni sesitsatfu futsi wahola iSt Mirren kusuka ekunciphiseni kuya ekutfoleni likiyo leligila umncintiswano lomnyaka lolandzelako.
Ross utsi utiva akhululekile kakhulu kunakucala ngesikhatsi adlala emaClyde, eHartlepool, eFolkerk, eSt Mirren naseHamilton Academical.
"Bekungatsi ngimi lengena embili", washo nakakhumbula kutsi sewungumceceshi we-Aloe.
"Bengikutsatsa njengentfo lencono kuba ngumceceshi kunekutsi ngibe ngumdlali.
Loko kuvakala kungakavami ngobe bengenta kahle kakhulu, ngenta imali lenyenti futsi ngite kakhulu.
Kodvwa kudlala kungaba matima.
Kumele ubeketelele lokunyenti njalo ngeliviki.
Ngisahlangabetana nekucindzeteleka kanye nekucindzeteleka emsebentini, kodvwa umsebenti wekucondzisa ungenta ngijabule.
Bengihlale ngifuna kuticecesha, futsi nyalo sengitiva nginekhululeke kakhulu kunakucala ekuphileni kwami".
Ungasilalela sonkhe lesicoco ku-Sportsound ngeLisontfo, Septhemba 30, nga-12:00-13:00 (Sunday, September 30)
Sikhatsi lesikahle sekunatsa tjwala ngu-5:30 kusihlwa ngeMgcibelo, ngekusho kwelucwaningo.
Kushisa kwehlobo kwacinisa imali yetinkampani letisebenta etindzaweni tekudlela taseBrithani, kodvwa kwafaka umfutfo lomkhulu etinkampanini tetindzawo tekudlela.
Emaphuphu kanye nemabha akhulisa kutsengiswa kwawo ngemaphesenti langu-2,7 ngaJuly, kodvwa imali yetindzawo tekudlela yehla ngemaphesenti langu-4.8, njengobe kubonisiwe.
Peter Martin, losesikhungweni sekubonisana ngemabhizinisi i-CGA, lowabhala lolucwaningo watsi: "Lokungapheli kwelilanga kanye nekubamba lichaza kweNgilandi kuNdzebe yeMhlaba, kwenta kutsi inyanga yaJuly ibenesimo lesifana nesenyanga lelandzelako, ngaJune, lapho khona imali yetitolo ikhula ngemaphesenti langu-2.8, kodvwa tindzawo tekudlela tona betihlaselwa kakhulu.
Kwehla kwemaphesenti langu-1.8 etinhlelweni tekudla ngaJuni kwabonakala kutsi sekwehle kakhulu ngaJuly.
Emaphuphu kanye nemabha lakhicita tjwala akwenta kahle kakhulu, ngetulu kwekukhula kwemabha lafana nawo eminyakeni leyengcile kunekwehla kwemabha lafana nawo etindzaweni tekudlela.
Imigwaco lephakela kudla nayo yahlupheka ngesikhatsi selusuku, kodvwa hhayi ngendlela lematima njengetindzawo tekudlela.
Kubonakala shengatsi bantfu bafuna nje kuphuma bayewunatsa tjwala.
Kuyo yonkhe imiphakatsi leyayisebenta, kukhicitwa kwetjwala kwakhula ngemaphesenti langu-6.6 ngenyanga, kantsi kudla kwehla ngemaphesenti lamatsatfu".
Paul Newman, losebenta ku-RSM, utsi: "Lemiphumela ikhombisa indlela lesesiyicondze kusukela ekupheleni kwa-April.
Sikhatsi kanye nemtselela wetintfo letinkhulu temphakatsi nobe temidlalo kusolo kungumtfombo lomkhulu wekutsengiswa kwemakethe yangaphandle.
Akumangalisi kutsi emacembu etitolo ayachubeka nekubhekana netinkinga, kepha kwehla kwemabhizinisi ngemaphesenti langu 4,8 ngemnyaka kutawuba buhlungu kakhulu ngenca yetinkinga letisolo tikhona.
Lenyanga lelishisa kakhulu yehlobo ayisifiki ngesikhatsi lesihle kubantfu labatsengisa kudla, futsi sikhatsi sitawuveta kutsi simo selitulu lesincane lesaba khona nga-Agasti sitawuphindze siphumelele yini".
Kukhula lokukhulu kwekutsengiswa kwemabha netindzawo tekudlela, kufaka ekhatsi emabhizinisi lamasha, kwaba ngu-2,7 ekhulwini ngaJulayi, lokukhombisa kwehla kwekwetfulwa kwemagama etitselo.
I-Coffer Peach Tracker yekutsengisa umkhakha wemabha, emabhara kanye netindzawo tekudlela e-UK icokelela iphindze ihlole imininingwane yekusebenta kahle kumacembu lamashumi lamane nesikhombisa, lanenzuzo lengetulu kwemali lengemarandi layinkhulungwane nemashumi layimfica, futsi iyinkhomba lesebentako kulomkhakha.
Umntfwana munye kulabasihlanu uba nema-akhawunti ekuchumana angatiwa batali bakhe
Lucwaningo lukhombisa kutsi umntfwana munye kulabasihlanu - ngisho nobe aneminyaka lengu-11 budzala - unema-akhawunti langatiwa emmangweni, angatiwa batali kanye nabothishela
Lucwaningo lolwentiwe kubantfwana besikolwa sebanga-20 000 lwaveta kutsi kunekukhula kwema-Instagram fake
Lokwatiswa kwaphindze kwaphakamisa kwesaba kutsi bantfu bayaveta kutsi banemacansi.
Emaphesenti langu-20 ebafundzi atsi anesikhwama "semagugu" labangatidlulisela kubatali babo
Lomunye kubantfwana labasihlanu - ngisho nobe aneminyaka lengu-11 budzala - usungula ema-akhawunti ekuchumana, futsi awagcinwa angatiwa ngulabanye bantfu labadzala.
Lucwaningo lolwentiwe kubantfu labangu-20 000 labasesikolweni lesiphakeme, lwembula kutsi kunekukhula lokukhulu kwema-akhawunti emanga e-Instagram.
Lokwatiswa kwaphindze kwabangela kwesaba lokukhulu kutsi bantfu bayababukela bantfu labasebancane.
Emaphesenti langemashumi lamabili ebafundzi atsi agcina "umholo" lomuhle kute akhombise batali bawo, aphindze agcine ema-akhawunti langasese.
Lomunye make lowatfola lelikhasi lelingasese lendvodzakati yakhe leneminyaka lengu-13 budzala, wabona intfombatana lebeyikhutsata labanye kutsi bayidlwengule ("ngidlwengule").
Lucwaningo lolwentiwe yi-Digital Awareness UK kanye ne-HMC yetikolo letitimele lutfole kutsi bafundzi labangemaphesenti langu-40 beminyaka lengu-11 kuya ku-18 banemaphrofayili lamabili, kantsi ihhafu yabo ivuma kutsi inemakhodi langatiwa.
UMengameli we-HMC, Mike Buchanan, watsi: "Kukhatsatekile kutsi bantfu labanyenti labaseminyakeni yekutfomba bayayekela kuvula ema-website lapho batali babo kanye nebafundzisi bangeke bakhone kubatfola khona".
Eilind Doyle utawuba livi lebadlali embutfweni weScotland's Track and Field Council
Eilind Doyle wakhetfwa kutsi abe lilunga le-Scotland Steering Committee emhlanganweni wemnyaka we-GMO.
Doyle ungumdlali welibhola letinyawo lohlonishwa kakhulu eScotland futsi Mengameli Ian Beattie utsite kukhetfwa kwakhe kuyindlela lenhle yekutsi labo labahola temidlalo batfole lwati lolunyenti lwekwati lokuningi lokwentiwe emhlabeni wonkhe kuleminyaka lelishumi leyengcile.
"Eilind uhlonishwa kakhulu kulo lonkhe leScotland, iBritish kanye nemhlabawonkhe, futsi sicinisekile kutsi iScotland itawuzuza kakhulu ngekungena kwakhe kulebhodi", kwasho Biti.
Doyle watsi: "Ngiyajabula kuba livi lebadlali bemidlalo futsi nginelitsemba lekutsi ngitawukwati kufaka sandla futsi ngisite ekuholeni temidlalo eScotland".
Lomuntfu waseMelika lowatfola indondo yeligolide kuma-200 naku-400 emidlalweni ye-Atlanta 1996 wawina ema-Olimpiki lamane, futsi nyalo sewungumhlabeli we-BBC, wagula kakhulu ngemuva kwekushaywa sifo semitsambo.
Watsi ku-Twitter: "Kwendlula inyanga yinye ngaba nesifo semsheko.
Bengehluleka ngisho nekuhamba.
Bodokotela batsi kutawuphela sikhatsi lesidze ngaphambi kwekutsi ngiphindze ngitive ngincono.
Bekudzinga emandla, kodvwa ngaphindze ngacala kuhamba futsi lamuhla sengiyakwati kuhamba.
Ngiyabonga kakhulu ngemilayeto yakho lesikhutsato!"
Sikhwama setilwane letifuywako lesifanisa bomake netinkhomo sihlukanisa bantfu ku-Internet
Inkampani lekhicita timbuti ihlukanise bantfu ku-Internet ngesikhangiso lesifanisa bomake labaniketa umntfwana wabo wemasikati netinkhomo letibaniketa lubisi.
Kute kukhulunywe ngalokutsiwa "ngumutsi wekucala longashoni futsi longasetjentiswa emhlabeni", inkampani yetetheknoloji ye-Elvie yakhipha sikhangiso lesitsatsekako lesitsatselwe etintfweni letitsite kute ikhombise inkhululeko leniketwa bomake labamunyisako.
Bomake labane labangababe bangena esitebeleni setinkhomo lesinetjani, bahlabela ingoma lenemagama latsi: "Yebo, ngiyatincengela, kodvwa awuboni ngisho nemsila" kanye naletsi "Uma ngabe awukaboni, loku akusiwo emabele ami, kodvwa ngito titsa tami".
Lelicembu liyachubeka: "Yidla, yifutfumele, nginika bantfwana kudla, yifutfumele, yifutfumele, yenta bafati bami babe mnandzi".
Nobe kunjalo, lesimemetelo lesishicilelwe ku-Facebook, sesivuse kuphikisana ku-inthanethi.
Ngalesikhatsi sekubukwa ema-77,000 futsi sekunemakhulu ema-comments, le-video itfole kuphendvuka lokungafani kubantfu lebebayibukela, njengobe labanyenti batsi ayiyitsatsi "ngemehlo" lemikhicito yelubisi.
"Kuncono kutsi usebentise tinkhomo kute ushayele umkhicito.
Njengaletinyoni, tidzinga kukhulelwa futsi tibeleke kute tikhone kukhicita lubisi, kodvwa bantfwana bato bayabaphuca lolubisi emalangeni lambalwa ngemuva kwekutalwa", kusho lomunye umtali.
Umntfwana wa-Elvie angahlala kahle esifubeni semuntfu lomunyisako (Elvie/Make)
Lomunye watsi: "Kubuhlungu kakhulu kumake naseluswaneni.
Kodvwa-ke, kungani singawasebentisi ekutsengiseni bomake labanebantfwana labangabafukamela?"
Lomunye wengeta watsi: "Sikhangiso lesingasilo liciniso".
Labanye bavikela lelikhangiso, kantsi lomunye wesifazane wavuma kutsi ingoma yakhe beyimnandzi.
"Ngicabanga kutsi ngumbono lomuhle.
Bengitawutsenga umntfwana lonjalo kube bengisolo ngisamunyisa.
Kupompa kwangenta ngativa nginjengenkhomo.
Lesikhangiso siyadideka, kodvwa angizange ngisicedze.
Umkhicito lohlakaniphile", kubhala lomunye.
Lomunye watsi: "Lesi sikhangiso lesihlekisako lesitsintsa bomake labatfola lubisi lwebuve (ngalokwetayelekile emsebentini nobe etindzaweni tekugeza) futsi bative 'njengaboti.'
Akusiyo ikhangiso leyenta bantfu badvumise nobe bagceke imboni yelubisi".
