Kutamatama kwemhlaba ne-tsunami e-Indonesia
Lokungenani bantfu labangu-384 babulawa kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kanye ne-tsunami leyahlaselwa edolobheni lase-Indonesia iPalu ngaLesihlanu, ngekusho kwemitfombo lesemtsetfweni, kantsi linani lebantfu labashonile kulindzeleke kutsi likhule.
Njengobe kuchubeka nekushabalala kwetekuchumana, tisebenti tetenhlalakahle atizange tikhone kutfola lwati lolutsite ku Donggala, indzawo lesenyakatfo yePalu, lesedvute nendzawo lapho kwavela khona kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokungu-7.5.
E-Palu, bantfu labangetulu kwa-16 000 basuswa ngemuva kwekugadla kwalenthlekelele.
Nati tintfo letibalulekile ngaPalu naDongala, eSulawesi:
IPalu iyinhloko-dolobha yesifundza sase Central Sulawesi, lesiseceleni kweligede lelimfisha lelisentshonalanga yelwandle lwesichingi sase Sulawesi, inebantfu labangu 379,800 nga 2017.
Lelidolobha belisandza kuhlanganisa iminyaka lengu-40 budzala ngesikhatsi kutamatama kwemhlaba kanye ne-tsunami kulihlasela.
I-Dongola yindzawo lencane lenemhlaba lenemhlaba longemakhilomitha langetulu kwa-300 (180 mi) ngaseningizimu-nshonalanga yeSulawesi.
Le-Vincoregio, lizinga lekuphatsa ngaphansi kwephondo, belinebantfu labalinganiselwa ku 299,200 nga-2017.
Kudvweba kanye nekulima ngito letisisekelo temnotfo wesifundza sase Central Sulawesi, ikakhulukati endzaweni yase Donggala leseceleni kwelwandle.
I-nickel mining nayo iyintfo lenkhulu esifundzeni, kepha itfolwa kakhulu eMorowali, ngaphesheya kweSulawesi.
I-Indonesia's Disaster Response Agency itsi iPalu neDonggala seyishaywe ngu-tsunami emahlandla lamanyenti kuleminyaka lelikhulu leyengcile.
Nga-1938, i-tsunami yabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-200 futsi yabhidlita emakhaya lamanyenti eDongala.
I-tsunami nayo yashaya i-Dongola leseNtshonalanga nga-1996, yabulala bantfu labangu-9.
I-Indonesia isendzaweni lenetikhukhula letinkhulu letise Pacific Ocean futsi ivame kuhlushwa kutamatama kwemhlaba.
Letinye tetindzawo letinkhulu letake tazamazama umhlaba kanye nema-tsunami, nguleti:
2004: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu e-Indonesia, enshonalanga ye-Aceh, enshonalanga yeSumatra, nga-December 26, kwabangela itsunami leyahlaselwa emaveni langu-14, yabulala bantfu labangu-226,000 elugwini lwe-Indian Ocean, ngetulu kwehhafu yabo bebakhona e-Aceh.
2005: Kuhlaselwa kwekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu elugwini lolusentshonalanga yeSumatra ekupheleni kwaMay nasekucaleni kwa-April.
Emahhala lamakhulu eNias Island, edvute neSumatra.
2006: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokungu-6.8 kwahlasela insimu yaseJawa, lokuyisichingi lesinelinyenti lebantfu e-Indonesia, kwabangela tsunami lowabhubhisa bantfu labangu-700 ngaseningizimu yelwandle.
2009: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla la-7.6 lokwenteka edolobheni lasePatang, lokuyinhloko-dolobha yaseSumatra leseNtshonalanga.
Bantfu labangetulu kwa-1 100 babulawa.
2010: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokungu-7.5 kusika sihlenge sihlenge saseMendawi, edvute naseSumatra, kwabangela tsunami lobukhulu bemamitha langu-10 leyacekela phansi emadolobhana lamanyenti futsi yabulala bantfu labangu-300.
2016: Kwenteka kutamatama kwemhlaba lokuncane endzaweni yase Pindi Jaya e-Atshekh, lokwabangela umonakalo kanye nekwesaba, kwaletsa tinkhulumo letinkhulu ngekubhujiswa lokwenteka nga-2004 ngekutamatama kwemhlaba lokwabulala bantfu labanyenti kanye ne-tsunami.
Ngalesikhatsi, akuzange kube khona tsunami, kodvwa bantfu labangetulu kwa-100 babulawa tigodlo letatiwile.
2018: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kwahlasela sihlenge lesitsandvwa tihambi saseLobok, e-Indonesia, kwabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-500, ikakhulukati enyakatfo yalesihlenge.
