Elite League: Dandi Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer wafaka umgoli webili kumaGiants kuDandy
I-Dandy Stars itsetse sihlengo sayo ngeLesihlanu ku-Elite League ku-Belfast Giants, ngekuncoba umchudzelwano nga-5-3 ku-Dandy ngeMgcibelo.
