Dwyer wavula umgoco ngemzuzu wesine nga 3:35 ngekusitwa ngu Kendall McFaul, ngesikhatsi David Rutherford asita Bowier kutsi aphindze abe nemandla emaminitsi lamane ngemuva kwaloko.
Ngesikhatsi sekusebenta kakhulu, Sullivan wafaka licembu lakhe le-volleyball emuva emdlalweni nga-13:10 ngaphambi kwekutsi Matt Marquard anikete Cooney lisito lekucedza lomdlalo nga-15:16.
Dwyer wacinisekisa kuhola kwemaGiants ngesikhatsi sekuphela kwencenye yekucala yemdlalo ngesikhatsi afinyelela umgomo wakhe wesibili ngalobo busuku.
Licembu lebadlali belibala lelidlalako lahlangana futsi Bousard waphindze walinganisa ngemagoli labonisa emandla, ngemzuzu wa-27: 37
Kaunie na Charles Corcoran bahlangana ndzawonye kute basite Nielsen kutsi anikete Dandi licebo lekuhola kwekucala emdlalweni ngasekupheleni kwesikhatsi sesibili, futsi wacinisekisa kuncoba kwakhe ngekugoma kwesihlanu kwelicembu lakhe emkhatsini wesikhatsi sekugcina.
Emadvodza aseGoli, lasebese alahlekelwe ngemidlalo lemine kulemihlanu leyengcile, adlala ekhaya kuMilton Keynes emdlalweni lolandzelako ngeLesihlanu.
Umhloli wetindiza ulahlekelwa kuphila kwakhe kute asindzise emakhulu ebagibeli be indiza
Umhloli wetindiza wase-Indonesia ubitwa ngekutsi yindvodza leyayincono, ngobe walahlekelwa kuphila kwakhe etama kuvikela indiza lebeyiphetse emakhulu ebantfu kutsi ingehli.
Bangetulu kwa-800 bantfu lababulewe futsi labanyenti bayanyamalala ngenca yekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwahlasela sihlenge saseSulawesi ngaLesihlanu, lokwabangela i-tsunami.
Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kuyachubeka nekubhubhisa lendzawo futsi bantfu labanyenti babhajwe tindvonga edolobheni lasePalu.
Nanobe labanye basebenti bakhe bebagijima basindzisa kuphila kwabo, Anthony Gunawan Agung loneminyaka lengu-21 budzala, wala kushiya sikhundla sakhe etinhlelweni tekuphatsa letatishayisana ngenhlitiyo ePalu's Mutiara Sis Al Jufri Airport.
Wahlala lapho kute acinisekise kutsi indiza ye-Batik Air Flight 6321, lebeyihamba ngalelitulu ngaleso sikhatsi, iyasuka ngekuphepha.
Ngemuva kwaloko, watsi uyagijima washiya umbhoshongo wekulawula ngesikhatsi acabanga kutsi utawubhidlika.
Wabese uyafa esibhedlela.
Umkhulumeli we Air Navigation Indonesia, Johannes Siret, watsi lesincumo singasindzisa imphilo yemakhulu, njengoba kubikwe yinethiwekhi yethelevishini i-ABC News yase-Australia.
Sase sitfumela lihholikhikhikhikhikhini lelisuka eBaliquipan eKalimantan kute liyomyisa esibhedlela lesikhulu lesikwelinye lidolobha.
Ngenhlanhla lembi, simlahlekelwe ngalelolanga ngaphambi kwekutsi le helikhodra ifike ePalu.
"Sikhungatsekile ngekushona kwakhe", wengeta.
Ngesikhatsi lesifanako, tiphatsimandla tesaba kutsi bantfu labanyenti bafile, kantsi nelihhovisi lelitiko lekulungisa tehlakalo kulelive litsi bantfu labanyenti abasakhoni kuya edolobheni lase Donggala, eSichi naseButung.
"Lelinani lebantfu labafile litawukhula, njengoba imitimba leminyenti isengcwabeni, futsi leminyenti yayo asikabi nayo", kusho Sotho Purgowo Ngroho, longumkhulumeli weliTiko Letasekhaya.
Emagagasi labengemamitha langu-20 ashaye phansi iPalu, letawufakwa emngcwabeni ngeLisontfo.
Imikhicito yemphi kanye neyetekuhweba iyahamba, futsi itfwala lusito netipho.
Reza Kuzuma, longumake loneminyaka lengu-35 budzala, watjela Sky News watsi: "Njalo ngemzuzu, imitsi yetemphilo iyaletsa tidvumbu.
Emanti lahlobile ayemancane.
Timakethe letincane tiphangwa yonkhe indzawo".
Jean Gelfant, longumengameli we-International Red Cross e-Indonesia, watjela i-CNN watsi: "Lemphakatsi we-Indonesian Red Cross uyachubeka nekusita bantfu labasindze, kodvwa asati kutsi yini labatawuyitfola.
Loko lokwenteka nyalo sekuyindzaba lenkhulu, kodvwa kungenteka kube yimbi kakhulu".
Mengameli we-Indonesia, Joko Widodo, wafika ePalu ngeLisontfo watsi ebutfweni lemasotja: "Ngicela kutsi nisebente busuku nemini kute nente yonkhe imisebenti lehlobene nekukhishwa kwebantfu.
Nilungele?" kusho i-CNN.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, ema-Indonesia ahlaselwa kutamatama kwemhlaba lokwenteka eLobok, lokwabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-550.
Kwehluleka kwe-Air Niugini kuchaza kutsi indvodza ayizange itfolakale ngemuva kwekushayisana kwendiza yayo echibini
Inkampani lendiza lebeyihamba indiza leyabhidlika elwandle loluselwandle loluselwandle lwase Pacific eMicronesia nyalo seyibika kutsi indvodza yinye iyalahleka, kantsi phambilini beyikhuluma kutsi bonkhe bantfu labangu-47 labebagibele kanye nebagibeli bayo besebahambe baphephile bayishiya lendiza lebeyiyacwila.
I-Air Niugini yatsi kulesimemetelo lesishicilelwe, kusukela ngaMgcibelo ntsambama beyingakhoni kutfola kutsi ngabe kukhona yini lokwentekile kulendvodza lebeyihamba kuyo.
Le nkapani yatsi isebenta netiphatsimandla tendzawo, tibhedlela kanye nebaphenyi kute batfole lendvodza.
Le nkapani ayizange iphendvule ngekushesha ticelo tekutfola imininingwane leminingi mayelana nemgibeli, lefaka ekhatsi iminyaka yakhe nobe buve bakhe.
Emakhumbi lasendzaweni asita ekuphuleni labanye bagibeli kanye nemalunga emtimba ngemuva kwekutsi lendiza ishaye emantini ngesikhatsi yetama kwehla esikhumulweni setindiza eChuck Island.
Tiphatsimandla titsi bantfu labasikhombisa batfunyelwe esibhedlela.
Inkampani yetindiza itsi bantfu labasitfupha labasitfupha bebasengakaphocelelwa kutsi bahambe, futsi bonkhe bebalungele kuboshwa.
Timbangela talokungevani kanye nekulandzelana kwetintfo letenteka, kusolo kungacaci.
Bobabili lenkapani kanye nelibutfo lemphi laseMelika batsi lendiza yabhaca elwandle lolungaphandle kwalendzawo yekwehla.
Labanye bofakazi beva kutsi lendiza yehlele phasi.
Umgibeli waseMelika, Bill Janes watsi lendiza yehla kakhulu.
"Loku kuhle kakhulu", kwasho Janes.
Jens watsi yena kanye nalabanye bakhona kuhamba emantini labekangenele kuze kube semkhatsini, baze bafika etindzaweni tekuphuma letidzinga lusito.
Watsi labantfu lebebalapho bebatfukutsele futsi bakhala futsi naye walimala kancane enhloko.
Lelisotja laseMelika lemphi latsi labanye bashayeli bemikhumbi lebebasebenta edvute nekulungisa indzawo yekubhukusha, nabo basita ekusiteni ngekusebentisa sikebhe lesivutako kute batfutse bantfu baye elusentseni ngaphambi kwekutsi umkhumbi wehlise emamitha lalikhulu.
Ngekusho kwe-Air Safety Network, bantfu labangu-111 bafile etimphini tetindiza ePapua New Guinea kuleminyaka lengemashumi lamabili leyengcile, kodvwa kute nakuyinye leyake yabulala i-Air Niugini.
