Umntfwana lonakekela bantfwana waseNew York wamangalela bantfu labashadene ngekubandlulula ngemuva kwekutfola umlayeto longakalungi lowatsatfwa ngunina, lowakhala ngekutsi lomntfwana lonakekela bantfwana "ungumuntfu lomnyama".
