Lindsey Plasco-Flaxman, longumake webantfwana lababili, wadvumala kakhulu ngesikhatsi atfola kutsi umnakekeli lomusha Giselle Morris, umnyama, ngemuva nje kwekutsi lomnakekeli lomusha avele ngelilanga lakhe lekucala emsebentini nga-2016.
"Kute Lenye Indvodza Lencono" kwabhala Make Plasco-Flaxman encwadzini layibhalela indvodza yakhe.
Kodvwa esikhundleni sekutsi ayitfumele kumyeni wakhe, wayitfumela kuMnumzane Morris kabili.
