Make Morris watfola imali yekusebenta lilanga linye, wase uyiswa ekhaya nge-Uber.
Nyalo-ke, make Morris ubeke lelicala lelibhekene nabo, afuna kutsi banikwe imali yekucitfwa, futsi ufuna kutsi banikwe imali lengemadola langu-350 ngelilanga, ngenca yemsebenti wakhe wekunakekela bantfwana labamunyako, lebekabekelwe wona, nanobe bekangenawo umcashi.
"Ngifuna kubakhombisa kutsi, uyabona, angeke ukhone kwenta intfo lenje", watjela i-Post ngaLesihlanu, watsi "Ngiyati kutsi loku kuyindlela yekuhlonipha".
Labantfu labashadene bayawaphikisa lamavi ekutsi baluhlanga, batsi bekunengcondvo kumcosha Morris ngobe bebesaba kutsi angeke baphindze bametsembe ngemuva kwekumhlazisa.
"Umfati wami wamtfumelela intfo langakafuni kuyitfumelela.
Akasiyo inhlanga.
