George Walker Bush ushayela emagama emalunga e-Senate, abaphocelela kutsi basekele Mnu. Kavanaugh, lobekasebenta kuNdlu yeMhlophe, futsi lowatiwa ngaye ngumkakhe Ashley, lobekangumabhalane waMnu. Bush.
