Linani lebantfu labangalaleli eNorth Korea liyancipha ngaphansi kwemandla aKim
Linani lebantfu labaphuma eNorth Korea baya eNingizimu Korea liyehla kusukela Kim Jong-un atsatsa bukhosi eminyakeni lesikhombisa leyengcile, kusho umtsetfo waseNingizimu Korea.
Park Byeong-seug, acaphuna imininingwane levela kuLitiko Letekuhlanganisa iNingizimu Korea, watsi bantfu labangu-1 127 balahlwa ngulesive ngemnyaka lophelile, kantsi nga-2011 bekunebantfu labangu-2 706.
UMnu Park watsi kuciniswa kwetinsita temincele emkhatsini weNorth Korea neChina kanye nekukhokhiswa kwetimali letiphakeme kubantfu labahamba ngetinyoni kwaba yintfo lemcoka.
Pyongyang ayikacali kukhuluma ngalendzaba.
Bantfu labanyenti labangafuni kuba boFakazi baseNyakatfo bebakhetfwa kutsi babe takhamuti taseNingizimu Korea.
E-Seoul, bantfu baseNyakatfo baseKorea labangetulu kwa-30 000 bebangene ngalokungekho emtsetfweni kulelive kusukela ekupheleni kweMphi yaseKorea nga-1953.
Linyenti labo libalekela eChina, lelinebantfu labanyenti labadzabuka eNyakatfo yeKorea, lelula kuyincoba kunalena levikeleka kakhulu emkhatsini weNyakatfo neNingizimu yeKorea.
I-China ibuka laba labangenele imphi njengebantfu labangenawo emtsetfweni kunekutsi ibaphatse njengebantfu lababalekile, futsi ivame kubacosha ngenkhani.
Budlelwane emkhatsini weNyakatfo neNingizimu Korea, lobusolo busemphini, sebuphucuke kakhulu etinyangeni letimbalwa letengcile.
Ekucaleni kwenyanga, baholi bemave lamabili bahlangana ePyongyang kute bacoce ngetingcoco tekucedza kukhinyabeteka kwemandla enyukliya.
Lomhlangano ulandzela umhlangano lobalulekile emkhatsini waMengameli waseMelika Donald Trump naKim Jong Un eSingapore, lapho bavumelana khona ngetimiso letinkhulu tekubambisana ekulweni nemacebo emayuniyamu aseNshonalanga yeKorea.
Kodvwa ngeMgcibelo, iNdvuna Yetepolitiki yaseNyakatfo yeKorea, Rim Jong Il, yatsi tikhungo teMelika tibangele kutsi kube nekungachubeki kahle kwekusebenta kwalelive.
"Ngaphandle kwekwetsemba iMelika, angeke kube nekwetsemba kuvikeleka kwetfu, futsi ngaphansi kwaletimo, angeke sikwati kucedza kucedza tikhali eveni letfu singasebenti", kwasho Reem nakakhuluma ku-UN General Assembly eNew York.
