Umengameli weNdlu yeTifundza, Nancy Pelosi, lobekalilunga le-Democratic Party, watsi Brett Kavanaugh, lotawuba lijaji leNkantolo lePhakeme, "uyadzabuka" futsi utsi ngekutiphatsa kabi akakulungeli kusebenta eNkantolo lePhakeme.
Pelosi washo lamavi ngesikhatsi ahlangana ne-Texas Tribune Festival e-Austin, eTexas, ngeMgcibelo.
