Waphindze walahla emaDemocrats labekakhona kulelikomidi, watsi letinsolo letimelene naye "tibulele bantfu ngekuhlukunyetwa futsi tihlelwe ngekuhleleka, lokuhlelwe ngema-liberal labekhatsateke ngekulahlekelwa ngu-Hillary Clinton elukhetfweni lwebuongameli lwanga-2016.
