Indlela imphi yekutsengisa yase US ne China lengenta ngayo lokuhle eBeijing
Imibono lejabulisako lemayelana nemphi yekutsengisa emkhatsini we-US ne-China beyimnandzi, kantsi futsi kusese sikhatsi lesidze kutsi imphi iphele, kodvwa kuphambana emkhatsini walamave lamabili kungazuzisa i-Beijing esikhatsini lesidze, kusho tati.
Mengameli waseMelika Donald Trump wakhipha sicwayiso sekucala ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, ngekubeka intsela etintfweni letibalulekile letitfunyelwa ngaphandle eChina, kufaka ekhatsi emaphaneli elanga, insimbi kanye ne-aluminium.
Lokunyenti kwavela kuleliviki, ngekubeka intsela lemisha etintfweni letingu-US$200 million (R290 million), lokusho kutsi, kuhlawuliswa kwemaphesenti lalishumi etintfo letingeniswa e-US kusuka eChina.
I-Beijing ivele ibuyisele umlilo ngalokungenani, futsi muva nje ibeke intsela lengemaphesenti lasihlanu kuya kulalishumi etintfweni letingu-R380 000 000 letitsengiswako.
I-China itimisele kuphindzisela kulesibhamu seMelika, futsi umnotfo wesibili lomkhulu emhlabeni angeke usicedze masinyane.
Kute akwati kwenta iWashington kutsi iwele, kufanele ivele ivele, kepha kukhonta eMelika kutawuba lihlazo lelikhulu ku-Xi Jinping, umengameli wase-China.
Kodvwa, ngekusho kwebahloli, uma iBeijing ingadlala kahle, kucindzetelwa kweMelika kulemphi yekutsengisa kungenta lokuhle kuChina esikhatsini lesidze ngekutsi kunciphise kuncike kuletinye temnotfo wato.
"Lokutsi sincumo lesitsite lesitsatfwe ngekushesha eWashington nobe eBeijing singabangela kuwohloka kwemnotfo kulamanye emave, kuyingoti kakhulu kwendlula indlela labanye lababuke tintfo labatibona ngayo", kusho Abigail Grace, longumcwaningi locwaninga nge-Asia ku-Center for New American Security, lokulibanga lekucabanga.
