Tonkhe timo setihlangabetiwe tekubuyiselwa ngekutitsandzela kwebabaleki labaphocelelwe kutsi babaleke ngenca yelubandlululo kanye netinyatselo tekubalekela umnotfo letitsintsa imphilo yabo yemalanga onkhe kanye netindlela tekutiphilisa.
